name: Onix Fira
address: Llançà, 30, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Onix Fira offers a small rooftop pool which is opened from April to October and is not heated, private parking and soundproofed rooms in Barcelona’s center, overlooking Joan Miró Park. name: TWO Hotel Barcelona by Axel 4* Sup- Adults Only
address: Calabria 90-92, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Offering a rooftop pool with a large sun terrace, TWO Hotel Barcelona by Axel is located in the heart of the gay district of Barcelona, 1.2 mi from Barceloneta Beach.', 'The hetero-friendly hotel offers on-site private parking. There is also a 24-hour reception and guests can get information on the gay scene and the city at the on-site tour desk. On the rooftop guests will also find the Sky bar, gym, steam bath and a massage room.', 'Each room here will provide you with air conditioning and a mini-bar. Featuring a shower, private bathroom also comes with a hairdryer. A safety deposit box and a universal phone charger are also provided.', 'Guests can sample a drink at the rooftop bar, while taking in stunning city views or enjoy the delicious cocktails served in the Lounge Bar. A buffet breakfast is available and free high-speed WiFi access is provided throughout.', 'Staff can give information about the surrounding area, which is known as "Gayxample" because of its lively gay nightlife.', "The hotel is 2 minutes' walk from Rocafort Metro Station and Plaça d'Espanya, with direct busses to Barcelona Airport, is a 10-minute walk away. Paral·lel, with bars, restaurants, clubs and theaters is 0.8 mi from TWO Hotel Barcelona by Axel."]

name: Entre la Estación y el Ayuntamiento
address: Convento Santa Clara, 6, Puerta 10, Ciutat Vella, 46001 Valencia, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in Valencia, a 3-minute walk from Valencia North Station, Entre la Estación y el Ayuntamiento provides accommodations with a terrace, free WiFi and a tour desk. Housed in a building dating from 1900, this apartment is a 12-minute walk from Church of Saint Nicolás and 1.8 km from Jardines de Monforte.', 'The apartment comes with 4 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, bed linen, towels, a flat-screen TV, a dining area, a fully equipped kitchen, and a balcony with city views.', 'Popular points of interest near the apartment include Turia Gardens, González Martí National Museum of Ceramics and Decorative Arts and Basilica de la Virgen de los Desamparados. The nearest airport is Valencia Airport, 10.9 km from Entre la Estación y el Ayuntamiento.']

name: Somnio Hostels
address: Diputacio, 251, 2, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This hostel, renovated in 2014, is set just a short distance from Las Ramblas, in the heart of Barcelona. It offers good value accommodations, in an ideal location for exploring the city.', 'Somnio Hostels is set next to Barcelona University. The famous buildings of Passeig de Gracia are just 200 m away. name: Urbany Hostel Barcelona
address: Avenida Meridiana, 97, Sant Martí, 08026 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Urbany Hostel Barcelona is on Barcelona’s Meridiana Avenue, 300 m from Clot Metro Station. This large, funky hostel has spacious common areas where you can relax and meet people from abroad. There are free Wi-Fi throughout and rooftop terrace with city views and bar service.', 'Each modern dormitory or room features lockers, an private bathroom and air conditioning.', 'The Urbany Barcelona serves a daily continental buffet breakfast. It has a kitchen with cookers, fridges and microwaves. There is a café-bar and vending machines, and you can request a packed lunch.', 'Staff at the 24-hour reception can provide information about what to see and do in Barcelona. Free city maps and tour information are available.', 'Urbany Hostel is 5 minutes’ walk from Glories Shopping Center, and Gaudí’s Sagrada Familia is a 15-minute walk away. You can reach the city center in 15 minutes by Metro or bus, and the beach is 1.2 mi away.']

name: Ofelias Hotel 4* Sup
address: Llançà, 24, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Ofelias Hotel 4* Sup! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set just off Gran Vía and a 2-minute walk from Plaza Espanya Metro Station and the Fira Exhibition Center, Ofelias Hotel offers stylish rooms with free Wi-Fi. It features a roof terrace with a seasonal outdoor swimming pool.', 'Each bright, air-conditioned room at Ofelias Hotel has a flat-screen TV. Each one comes with a private bathroom. A free bottle of water is provided upon arrival.', 'The hotel has an on-site bar where you can get a drink. There is a range of cafes and bars around Plaza Espanya. Restaurants can be found on Las Ramblas and in the Gothic Quarter, just 4 Metro stops away.', 'Staff at the reception can give you information about different Slow Travel activities .These include free bicycles on request, allowing you to discover hidden places and enjoy local cultures. .', 'The Magic Fountains and Montjuïc Park are less than 0.6 mi from the Ofelias, and Las Arenas Shopping center is just opposite the hotel. The airport bus stops just 200 m from the hotel. Bicycle rental is available on request from reception.']

name: Urbany Hostel BCN GO!
address: Gran Via de les Corts Catalanes, 563, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Featuring a rooftop terrace with jacuzzi, a fully equipped kitchen and computers with internet access, Urbany Hostel BCN GO! is set in the heart of Barcelona, just 200 m from Plaza Universitat Square.', 'Both shared dorms and private rooms are available, all with air conditioning, free Wi-Fi and bed linen. Each bed has a locker, a reading light, bedside table, a USB charger and 2 plugs. Laundry facilities and towels are available for an extra cost.', 'Urbany Bar serves drinks and food and there are also vending machines for snacks. A wide range of dining options and bars can be found in the surrounding area.', 'Staff can help with tourist information and also organize activities in the hostel and around Barcelona city. Luggage storage is available at the hostel.', 'Airport buses leave from Plaza Catalunya, which is a 10-minute walk from Urbany Hostel.']

address: Calabria 90-92, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Offering a rooftop pool with a large sun terrace, TWO Hotel Barcelona by Axel is located in the heart of the gay district of Barcelona, 1.2 mi from Barceloneta Beach.', 'The hetero-friendly hotel offers on-site private parking. There is also a 24-hour reception and guests can get information on the gay scene and the city at the on-site tour desk. On the rooftop guests will also find the Sky bar, gym, steam bath and a massage room.', 'Each room here will provide you with air conditioning and a mini-bar. Featuring a shower, private bathroom also comes with a hairdryer. A safety deposit box and a universal phone charger are also provided.', 'Guests can sample a drink at the rooftop bar, while taking in stunning city views or enjoy the delicious cocktails served in the Lounge Bar. A buffet breakfast is available and free high-speed WiFi access is provided throughout.', 'Staff can give information about the surrounding area, which is known as "Gayxample" because of its lively gay nightlife.', "The hotel is 2 minutes' walk from Rocafort Metro Station and Plaça d'Espanya, with direct busses to Barcelona Airport, is a 10-minute walk away. Paral·lel, with bars, restaurants, clubs and theaters is 0.8 mi from TWO Hotel Barcelona by Axel."]

name: Casa Gracia
address: Passeig de Gracia, 116 Bis, Gràcia, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Casa Gracia! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Casa Gràcia is a modern hostel at the top of Barcelona’s Passeig de Gràcia, 300 m from Gaudí’s La Pedrera. It offers air-conditioned rooms and free Wi-Fi in all areas.', 'Shared and private rooms are available, as well as apartments. Facilities at Casa Gràcia include a communal terrace, lounge, kitchen, dining area and a 24-hour front desk.', 'The hostel arranges daily walking tours of the city.', 'Casa Gràcia is located just yards from Avinguda Diagonal and within 300 m of Diagonal Metro Station, which offers access to the Sagrada Familia.', 'Passeig de Gràcia is full of exclusive shops, restaurants and bars. Gaudí’s Casa Batlló is within a 10-minute walk, as well as the popular Gràcia neighborhood. There are a number of beautiful Modernist buildings in the area.']

name: Onix Fira
address: Llançà, 30, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Onix Fira offers a small rooftop pool which is opened from April to October and is not heated, private parking and soundproofed rooms in Barcelona’s center, overlooking Joan Miró Park. Lively Plaza Espanya is 200 m away and offers a direct connection to Ramblas.', 'All of the spacious rooms in the Onix Fira come with free Wi-Fi, a modern décor and a private bathroom. They include a safe, mini-bar and telephone.', 'A number of restaurants and bars can be found within a 15-minute walk from the Onix Fira Hotel.', 'Montjuïc and the Magic Fountains are less than a 10 minutes’ walk away from Fira. The airport bus and Fira Exhibition Center are 200 m away.', 'Please, be aware that swimming pool is not heated and will be opened from April to October.']

name: Travelodge Barcelona Poblenou
address: Llull, 170, Sant Martí, 08005 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description:
['This modern hotel has 250 spacious and fully equipped rooms, a Snack-Bar open 24 hours where clients can enjoy a buffet breakfast, as well as light meals for lunch and dinner. It also has vending machines and private paid parking. All its facilities are perfectly adapted and accessible for people with reduced mobility.
It is a hotel with free and unlimited high-speed Wi-Fi in the common areas. Wi-Fi internet is available in the rooms at an extra cost.
Travelodge Barcelona Poblenou is a pet-friendly hotel that will be happy to offer you and your pet the best experience.
It is located in the traditional Poblenou neighborhood, within streets full of restaurants, bars and shops. One of the most charming neighborhoods in the city, and 601 m from the Bogatell beach. Barcelona city center can be reached in 10 minutes by metro and Barcelona’s Port Olímpic, with its vibrant night life, is just a 20-minute walk away.
This is considered the most innovative neighborhood in the city. It´s in the heart of the 22@ District and concentrates a multitude of technology and R+D companies. Therefore, thanks to its location and facilities, it is also a perfect accommodations for business trips.
Travelodge Barcelona Poblenou offers all you need to have the best experience in Barcelona city.']

name: Hostel New York
address: Gignas, 6-8, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hostel New York is a youth hostel located in Barcelona’s Gothic Quarter, 5 minutes’ walk from Las Ramblas. It offers 24-hour reception and free WiFi, 500 m from Jaume and Drassanes Metro Stations.', 'The hostel’s simple dormitory rooms feature modest décor, bunk beds and individual lockers. They include access to a shared bathroom; and free bed linen are provided.', 'There is a kitchen available for guests in the evenings and a TV lounge with vending machines selling drinks and snacks. There are also 2 computers.', "New York is ideally located for visiting many of Barcelona’s sights by foot. Ciutadella Park is a 10-minute walk away and Barceloneta Beach is 15 minutes's walk away.", '']

name: Pensión Villanueva
address: Plaza Real, 2, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Centrally located in one of the most charming areas of the historic center of Barcelona, Pension Villanueva is located 100 m from la Rambla. It offers comfortable accommodations with city views and free WiFi.', 'All rooms Pension Villanueva are soundproofed, and guests have access to either a shared bathroom or a private bathroom. Some rooms have a balcony and some have views of the Rambla or of Plaça Reial Square.', 'Other facilities offered include luggage storage.', 'Pension Villanueva is 901 m from Plaça Catalunya is surrounded by shops, restaurants, and café bars. Camp Nou is 2.8 mi away and the beaches of Barceloneta are a 5-minute drive from the property. Barcelona Airport is at a distance of 7.5 mi.']

name: Apartaments-Hotel Hispanos 7 Suiza
address: Sicilia, 255, Eixample, 08025 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["Hispanos 7 Suiza offers luxury apartments with two bathrooms decorated with wooden floors and elegant oak furniture, located 100 m from Gaudí's Sagrada Familia Basilica. Accommodations feature free Wi-Fi and a private balcony.", 'The hotel reception is open 24 hours and offers various services such as car rental, tourist information and ticket sales. The apartments are cleaned weekly or on request.', 'In the basement of the Apartamentos Hispanos 7 Suiza there is an impressive and unique exhibition of classic cars from the early 20th century of the Barcelona brand.', 'Also in our lobby they have one of the best food markets in the region. Where you will find any local fresh product. Km0.', 'The apartments are about 100 m from Sagrada Familia Metro Station. Barcelona Airport is a 20-minute drive away.']

name: Acta Voraport
address: Carrer de Ramon Turró 169-B, Sant Martí, 08005 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in Barcelona, a 10-minute walk from Bogatell Beach, Acta Voraport has accommodations with a restaurant, private parking, an outdoor swimming pool and a bar. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and an ATM, along with free WiFi throughout the property. Guests can have a drink at the snack bar.', 'The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a desk, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower. At Acta Voraport the rooms are equipped with bed linen and towels.', 'A buffet breakfast is available every morning at the accommodation.', 'Acta Voraport has a sun terrace.', 'Popular points of interest near the hotel include Mar Bella Beach, Nova Icaria Beach and Somorrostro Beach. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 19.3 km from Acta Voraport.']

name: Cosmo Apartments Consell de Cent - Plaza Universitat
address: Consell de Cent, 207, Eixample, 08011 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Cosmo Apartments Consell de Cent - Plaza Universitat! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located 701 m from central Barcelona’s Universitat Square, this property offers stylish, well-equipped apartments. It is 300 m from Urgell Metro Station, just 2 stops from Las Ramblas and Plaza de Catalunya.', 'Each air-conditioned apartment has chic, contemporary décor with chrome finishes and trendy furnishings. The living room has a sofa, a flat-screen TV and an iPod docking station.', 'The kitchen includes an electric hob, an oven, microwave, dishwasher and a kettle. There is also a dining area.', 'Shops, bars and cafés can be found in the streets surrounding the apartments and on Universitat Square, 10 minutes’ walk away.', 'The apartments are within 0.9 mi of Barcelona’s Gothic Quarter, the Raval District and the CCCB Art Gallery. Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard and the famous Gaudí houses can be reached in just 10 minutes by Metro.', 'The airport bus stops 150 m away, while Sants Railway Station and the AVE High-Speed Train are easily accessed by Metro from the nearby Catalunya Station.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Sagrada Familia! name: Onix Liceo
address: Nou de la Rambla, 36, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Onix Liceo is next to Gaudi’s Palau Guell, 300 m from Liceo Metro Station on Barcelona’s Ramblas. This stylish hotel offers a sun terrace and free Wi-Fi access.', 'The Onix is a design hotel with modern art in its public spaces. There is also a lounge and a business center.', 'Free water, coffe and tea are available 24 hours a day.', 'All air-conditioned rooms at the Onix are spacious and elegant. They have a mini-bar and LCD satellite TV. The private bathroom is equipped with a hairdryer.', 'You can hire a car or bicycle from the hotel tour desk. There is a 24-hour reception and a laundry service.', 'Please, be aware that swimming pool is not heated and will be opened from April to October.']

name: Andante Hotel
address: Avenida de les Drassanes, 23-25, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['With a small rooftop pool offering great views over Barcelona, Andante Hotel is centrally located 350 m from Drassanes Metro Station and La Rambla. It offers free Wi-Fi and a gym.', 'Modern air-conditioned rooms feature parquet floors, a laptop safe and flat-screen satellite TV. The bathroom comes with a full-length mirror and a high-powered hairdryer.', 'A buffet breakfast with show cooking is available. A gluten-free breakfast is available upon request. There is a self-service area with a microwave and vending machines for drinks, sandwiches and snacks, as well as a large terrace.', 'You can hire a car from the tour desk and a private shuttle from and to Barcelona El Prat Airport is available on prior request at an extra cost. There is a luggage storage room and a laundry and ironing service are offered.']

name: Hotel Oasis
address: Pla Del Palau,17, Ciutat Vella, 08003 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hotel Oasis is located just 250 m from França Railway Station and 100 m from Barcelona’s Born district. The modern, air-conditioned rooms have satellite TV and private bathrooms with hairdryer.', "The hotel features a seasonal terrace with a seasonal outdoor pool. The hotel's Oasis café-bar offers a range of hot drinks and cocktails throughout the day.", 'The beach and bars of Barceloneta are just 200 m away, while Santa Maria del Mar Church is 4 minutes’ walk away. Oasis is 50 m from Barceloneta Metro Station, and 300 m from Ciutadella Park.']

name: HCC Taber
address: Aragón, 256, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located just an 8-minute walk from central Barcelona’s Plaza Catalunya, Hotel HCC Taber is housed in an impressive Modernist building. It has air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi.', 'The rooms at HCC Taber feature satellite TV and a minibar. The private bathroom includes a hairdryer and free toiletries.', 'The building of the HCC Taber was originally designed by the famous Barcelona architect, Domènech i Montaner, who also designed the amazing Palau de la Música Catalana. It still retains its characteristic wrought-iron balconies and large bay windows.', 'The hotel’s buffet breakfast serves a wide range of dishes, and there are also breakfast options from the menu. There is also a snack bar and room service.', 'The Ramblas are just a 10-minute walk from the hotel, and Gaudí’s iconic Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are also within a 10-minute walk. Airport buses leave from Plaza Catalunya.']

name: HCC Taber
address: Aragón, 256, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located just an 8-minute walk from central Barcelona’s Plaza Catalunya, Hotel HCC Taber is housed in an impressive Modernist building. It has air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi.', 'The rooms at HCC Taber feature satellite TV and a minibar. The private bathroom includes a hairdryer and free toiletries.', 'The building of the HCC Taber was originally designed by the famous Barcelona architect, Domènech i Montaner, who also designed the amazing Palau de la Música Catalana. It still retains its characteristic wrought-iron balconies and large bay windows.', 'The hotel’s buffet breakfast serves a wide range of dishes, and there are also breakfast options from the menu. There is also a snack bar and room service.', 'The Ramblas are just a 10-minute walk from the hotel, and Gaudí’s iconic Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are also within a 10-minute walk. Airport buses leave from Plaza Catalunya.']

name: HCC Montblanc
address: Vía Laietana, 61, Ciutat Vella, 08003 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Set in the Gothic Quarter and next to Urquinaona Metro Station, HCC Montblanc offers air-conditioned rooms, free Wi-Fi, satellite TV and a mini-bar.', 'Guests can enjoy a varied buffet breakfast and à la carte Mediterranean cuisine in El Racó del Montblanc restaurant.', 'Close to the Born district, Hotel Montblanc Barcelona is a 10-minute walk from Barcelona Cathedral and 500 m from Plaza de Catalunya. Palau de la Musica Concert Hall, a UNESCO World Heritage Site, is just 250 m away.', 'City tour busses and direct busses to Barcelona Airport stop at Plaza Catalunya.']

name: Leonardo Hotel Barcelona Gran Via
address: Diputacio, 100, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This spacious and modern hotel is located in Eixample district, built in 2004, the Leonardo Hotel Barcelona Gran Via, features wide-open public spaces covered in marble.', 'Rooms include flat-screen TV, Wifi, safebox, desk, mini-bar, private bathrooms with toiletries.', 'A good location for tourism, you can easily walk to the Gothic Quarter and Ramblas, or up to the attractions of Montjuic. The city’s major business districts are also nearby.', 'Rooms include satellite TV, free Wi-Fi access, air conditioning and a bathroom with free toiletries.', 'Parking is available on site at an additional cost.']

name: Hotel Sant Agustí
address: Plaça Sant Agusti, 3, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Open since 1840, Sant Agustí is set in a restored convent just 150 m from Barcelona’s famous Las Ramblas. It offers free Wi-Fi and functional air-conditioned rooms with flat-screen satellite TV.', 'Each room at Hotel Sant Agustí has simple, modern design and wooden flooring. Rooms come with a safe and a bathroom with toiletries and a hairdryer. Some rooms have a private balcony.', 'The Sant Agustí serves a daily continental buffet breakfast.', 'Downstairs there are computers which guests can use for free. Reception is also open 24 hours a day.', 'Set in a quiet square, the hotel is a 2-minute walk from Liceu Metro Station and La Boqueria Market. Plaza Catalunya is within 701 m and offers various bus and train connections, including direct airport busses.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Weflating Sant Antoni Market! name: Hotel Via Augusta
address: Vía Augusta, 63, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08006 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Situated next to Gràcia FGC Train Station, Hotel Via Augusta has a rooftop terrace with views of Barcelona. It offers functional, air conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi and flat-screen satellite TV.', 'The Via Augusta is a historic building with a beautiful original foyer. Rooms have simple, modern décor and hardwood floors. They include a work desk, a safe and a bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'A varied breakfast buffet is served in the hotel, and drinks are available from the vending machine. A wide range of bars and restaurants can be found in the popular Gràcia district, within a 5-minute walk.', 'Hotel Via Augusta is 397 m from Fontana Metro Station, and Parc Güell is just 1 Metro stop away. Plaza Catalunya and Las Ramblas are a 5-minute ride from nearby Gracia Station.']

name: Olivia Plaza Hotel
address: Plaza de Catalunya, 19, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located on Plaza Catalunya in the center of Barcelona, the Hotel Olivia Plaza offers free Wi-Fi and a terrace bar with views of Santa Ana Church. Stylish rooms include a flat-screen TV.', 'This design hotel serves a buffet breakfast and guests can also order breakfast to the room. The modern Nineteen restaurant offers Mediterranean cuisine.', 'The chic rooms at the Olivia Hotel Barcelona include a free safe and views over the square. They are also equipped with a sofa or armchair and a breakfast table.', 'Guests at Olivia Plaza Hotel have free access to Holmes Place Urquinaona gym, located 500 m from the hotel. Guests can make free use of the pool area and fitness room there.', 'The Olivia Plaza Barcelona is just 100 m from the famous Ramblas with its many restaurants and street performers. Catalunya Metro Station is 2 minutes’ walk from the hotel and the Gothic Quarter is less than 10 minutes away.']

name: Novotel Barcelona City
address: Avenida Diagonal 201, Sant Martí, 08018 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This hotel offers a free gym and a roof terrace with a seasonal outdoor pool and panoramic views of Barcelona. The rooms include free Wi-Fi and flat-screen satellite TV.', 'Novotel Barcelona City is located next to Glòries Shopping Center and the Glories Tower, designed by Jean Nouvel. The Sagrada Familia Basilica and Bogatell Beach are both a 20-minute walk away.', 'The air-conditioned rooms at Novotel Barcelona City have simple, modern décor. Up to 2 children under 16 stay for free when sharing with parents.', 'The hotel’s restaurant offers characteristic Mediterranean food.', 'On the rooftop there is an outdoor swimming pool and a gourmet bar where guests can enjoy tapas, wines and cocktails enjoying panoramic city views.', 'Staff at reception are happy to provide information about Barcelona. Tram and bus services to the city center stop outside the hotel. Glòries Metro Station is just 300 m away.']

name: Hotel Sagrada Familia
address: Córcega, 541, Eixample, 08025 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located just 2 blocks from the Sagrada Familia, this hotel has a rooftop terrace overlooking Gaudí’s world-famous temple. It offers 24-hour reception and rooms with satellite TV and free Wi-Fi.', 'The air-conditioned rooms at the Hotel Sagrada Familia feature parquet floors and modern furniture. They are equipped with a mini-bar and the private bathrooms come with a hairdryer.', 'Glòries Shopping Center and Arc de Triomf are under 20 minutes’ walk from the hotel. Sagrada Familia Metro Station, located a 3-minute walk away, connects you with the city center in 5 minutes.']

name: Hotel Villa Emilia
address: Calabria, 115-117, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This stylish design hotel is located 150 m from Rocafort Metro Station in Barcelona. It offers a trendy rooftop bar and air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi and plasma satellite TV.', 'The soundproofed rooms at Hotel Villa Emilia feature parquet floors and modern décor. Each one has a mini-bar and a private bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'Hotel Villa Emilia Barcelona’s restaurant serves creative Catalan food, and there is a weekly barbecue. The Villa Emilia Bistrot offers live music.', 'Staff at the hotel’s 24-hour reception can provide information about what to see and do in Barcelona. There are also car and bicycle rental services at the front desk.', 'Hotel Villa Emilia is just 10 minutes’ walk from Plaza Espanya, where you can find the Fira Convention Center. Sants Station is 15 minutes’ walk away.']

hotel_description: ['Located in Barcelona, a 7-minute walk from Magic Fountain of Montjuic, Hotel Brick Barcelona features views of the city. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 12.1 km from the hotel.']

address: Valldonzella, 5, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Mesón Castilla is set just 100 m from Las Ramblas and Plaça Catalunya Square in central Barcelona. The hotel provides free Wi-Fi and an attractive terrace where guests can enjoy breakfast.', 'Rooms at the Mesón Castilla include ornate beds, and some have a private balcony. They come with air conditioning and a private bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'The hotel operates a 24-hour front desk, allowing guests flexibility during their stay. The tour desk can organize excursions and car rental. There are safes available at the reception for an extra charge.', 'Barcelona’s Modern Art Museum is a 5-minute walk from the hotel. The historic Gothic Quarter, with its cathedral and many bars, can be reached in 10 minutes by foot.']

name: St Christopher's Inn Barcelona
address: Bergara, 3, Eixample, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Just a 2-minute walk from La Rambla, St Christopher’s Inn Barcelona offers stylish air-conditioned accommodations with free Wi-Fi and a 24-hour reception. This modern backpackers’ hostel has a bar-restaurant, serving continental breakfast.', 'The bright dormitory rooms feature large windows and functional décor. Each one includes bunk beds with privacy curtains and fresh bed linen on arrival. Towels can be rented from reception.', 'The St Christopher’s Hostel Barcelona includes Belushi’s bar-restaurant, serving a range of meals, snacks and drinks, with special discounts for guests. name: Acta Splendid
address: Muntaner, 2, Eixample, 08011 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Acta Splendid is located in central Barcelona, 5 minutes’ walk from Plaza Catalunya and Las Ramblas. It offers 24-hour reception and air-conditioned rooms with satellite TV and free Wi-Fi.', 'Staff at the Hotel Splendid’s 24-hour reception can help booking tickets for guided tours, live shows and other events. There is also a computer in the lobby that guests can use for free.', 'There is a public car park 450 m from the hotel, around a 7-minute walk. You can walk to the Palau de la Música Catalana, a Modernist auditorium and UNESCO World Heritage Site, in 15 minutes.', 'Gluten-free breakfasts are available upon request.']

name: Sunotel Aston
address: Paris, 101, Eixample, 08029 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Featuring a rooftop terrace with a seasonal swimming pool and hot tub, as well as panoramic views of Barcelona, Sunotel Aston is a 3-minute walk from Hospital Clinic Metro Station.', 'Air-conditioned rooms include a flat-screen TV, soundproofed windows and a private bathroom with a hairdryer. Free, high-speed WiFi is available.', 'An extensive buffet breakfast is served at the hotel. The hotel’s Maya Restaurant offers a wide selection of dishes from around the world. There are also many eating options in the area.', 'Sunotel Aston has a 24-hour reception and offers services such as luggage storage, free pool towels and free bikes.', 'Plaza Catalunya and the Ramblas can be reached in around 15 minutes by public transport; while Barcelona’s famous Sagrada Familia Cathedral is around 10 minutes away.']

name: Hotel & Spa Villa Olimpica Suites
address: Pallars, 121-125, Sant Martí, 08018 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This minimalist hotel is located in the Poble Nou district of Barcelona, 15 minutes’ by foot from Bogatell Beach. It offers a seasonal outdoor pool surrounded by attractive wooden decking and loungers.', 'The chic suites at Hotel & Spa Villa Olimpic@ feature monochrome decoration and a flat-screen TV. They also include air conditioning and a modern bathroom.', 'The Hotel & Spa Villa Olimpic@ Suites complex offers a stylish café-bar and restaurant. Guests can enjoy Mediterranean cuisine from the á la carte and daily menus. In summer meals can be enjoyed on the terrace by the pool.', "Guests have access to the hotel's large spa for an additional cost. It includes an indoor treatment pool, Finnish sauna, Turkish baths, hot tubs, several types of shower and an ice fountain. There is also a gym.", "Barcelona Port is 15 minutes' walk away and Bogatell Metro Station is 100 m from the hotel. Guests can walk to the lively Villa Olimpica area in 5 minutes.", '']

name: Acta BCN 40
address: Joaquin Costa, 40, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Acta BCN 40 Hotel is centrally located 350 m from Barcelona’s Plaza Universitat, and a 5-minute walk from the Ramblas. It offers modern rooms with flat-screen satellite TVs.', 'Rooms at the Acta are air-conditioned in summer and heated in winter, and have a free safe. The private bathroom comes with a hairdryer and amenities, and you can request an iron at reception.', 'Guests can enjoy a varied buffet breakfast in the hotel’s stylish breakfast room. A gluten-free breakfast is available upon request. There are many bars, shops and restaurants within a short walk of the hotel.', 'The Acta BCN 40 has a 24-hour front desk and offers luggage storage. Parking is available nearby for an extra charge.']

name: Occidental Atenea Mar - Adults Only
address: Paseo García Faria, 37-47, Sant Martí, 08019 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located 150 m from Barcelona’s Nova Mar Bella Beach, Occidental Atenea Mar - Adults Only offers sauna and gym, and a free WiFi zone. Each air-conditioned room features international satellite TV.', 'The hotel features a terrace with sea views and a seasonal infinity pool with hydromassage beds and seats. You can rent Balinese beds and sun loungers. There is also a seasonal snack bar, which is open from June to September.', 'Occidental Atenea Mar - Adults Only offers bright, functional rooms, many with views of the city or sea. They include a mini-bar, a free safe and a private bathroom with amenities.', 'The hotel’s Canela restaurant serves à la carte Mediterranean meals, and a varied breakfast buffet is available each morning. There are also many bars and restaurants on the nearby seafront promenade.', 'Regular bus services to central Barcelona stop outside the Occidental Atenea Mar - Adults Only, while Poble Nou Metro Station is a 10-minute walk away. The CCIB Conference Center and Diagonal Mar Shopping Center are just 0.6 mi from the hotel.']

name: Catalonia Avinyo

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Avinyo! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located 200 m from Las Ramblas in central Barcelona, Catalonia Avinyo features a rooftop pool and gym. The Liceu and Jaume I Metro Stations are just 300 m away and Barcelona Cathedral is 4 minutes' walk away.", 'The Avinyo’s central location means there are many shops, bars and restaurants close to the hotel. Bicycle and car hire can be arranged at the tour desk.']

name: Hotel Peninsular
address: Carrer de Sant Pau, 34, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel Peninsular! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Just a one minute walk from Las Ramblas, this charming hotel features a free Wi-Fi zone and a bright central courtyard filled with plants. Liceu Metro Station is only 202 m away.', 'Hotel Peninsular features functional, air-conditioned rooms with private bathrooms. The hotel’s 24-hour front desk offers luggage storage and information about Barcelona.', 'The Peninsular is on the edge of the trendy Raval district, which is full of lively bars. The colorful street performers and sidewalk cafés of Las Ramblas are just around the corner.', 'The famous Boqueria Market is 247 m from the hotel, while Barcelona Cathedral is 0.5 km away. Airport buses and local trains stop in Plaça Catalunya, a 10-minute walk away.']

name: Silken Sant Gervasi
address: Sant Gervasi de Cassoles, 26, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08022 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in the quiet San Gervasi district of Barcelona, this elegant hotel offers modern rooms with free internet connection. The Silken is just 8 minutes by train from Plaza Catalunya.', 'The restaurant at Silken San Gervasi offers traditional cuisine with modern influences. A breakfast buffet is served in the cafeteria, and drinks and snacks are also available throughout the day.', 'Functional rooms include a free safe and central heating and air conditioning. The marble bathroom is complete with a hairdryer.', 'Silken St. Gervasi is a 15-minute walk from Park Guell, with impressive structures, mosaics and architecture by Antoni Gaudí. El Putxet Station can be found 50 m from the hotel with direct access to the city center.']

name: Hostal Operaramblas
address: Sant Pau, 20, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hostal Operaramblas is less than 100 m from Las Ramblas and Liceu Metro Station. This guesthouse features rooms with private bathrooms, a 24-hour front desk and free Wi-Fi.', 'The Operaramblas’ rooms have simple décor with tile floors. Each room has heating and a telephone.', 'The guesthouse has a drinks machine and sells snacks in the lobby, where there is also a computer with internet access.', 'The guesthouse has an ideal location in the center of Barcelona. It is a 5-minute walk from the Gothic Quarter, where there are a range of cafes, bars and restaurants. The city’s cathedral is just over a quarter mile from the Opera and the Old Port is less than a 10-minute walk away.']

name: Silken Sant Gervasi
address: Sant Gervasi de Cassoles, 26, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08022 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in the quiet San Gervasi district of Barcelona, this elegant hotel offers modern rooms with free internet connection. The Silken is just 8 minutes by train from Plaza Catalunya.', 'The restaurant at Silken San Gervasi offers traditional cuisine with modern influences. A breakfast buffet is served in the cafeteria, and drinks and snacks are also available throughout the day.', 'Functional rooms include a free safe and central heating and air conditioning. The marble bathroom is complete with a hairdryer.', 'Silken St. Gervasi is a 15-minute walk from Park Guell, with impressive structures, mosaics and architecture by Antoni Gaudí. El Putxet Station can be found 50 m from the hotel with direct access to the city center.']

name: Catalonia Atenas
address: Avenida Meridiana, 151, Sant Martí, 08026 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Atenas! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set 3 metro stops from central Barcelona, the Atenas Catalonia has a rooftop swimming pool, offering views of the nearby Torre Agbar and Sagrada Familia. It also features free WiFi, a gym and a spa with a Turkish bath.', 'The bright rooms of Hotel Atenas Barcelona have simple décor with wooden flooring. Each has air conditioning, a mini fridge with complimentary water, and satellite TV.', "The hotel's buffet breakfast features a show kitchen. There is a snack bar and guests can enjoy stunning city views from the pool, set on the 11th floor.", 'The Sagrada Familia is just over one kilometer from the hotel, while Glòries shopping center can be reached in 15 minutes by foot.', 'The Catalonia Atenas has a convenient left luggage service, on-site parking, and is 2 minutes’ walk from Clot Metro Station; and 200 m from Clot Train Station; here you can take a direct train to Barcelona Airport.']

name: Best Western Premier Hotel Dante
address: Mallorca, 181, Eixample, 08036 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['The Best Western Premier Dante is located in the Eixample district of Barcelona, a few minutes walking from the elegant Paseo de Gracia, Plaza de Catalunya and the famous Pedrera and Casa Batlló. With a functional design, the Hotel has a Lobby Bar, meeting rooms, internet corner and private parking.', 'The rooms are spacious and daylight. They have free WI-FI connection, coffee maker, electronic safe, LCD satellite TV and air conditioning, as well as a complete bathroom. The Suites are located on the 7th floor and have a large terrace with views of Barcelona.', "The Buffet Breakfast offers a wide variety of milk and vegetable drinks, juices, coffees, infusions, pastries and salty. Many of the products served are gluten free. The Hotel's Lobby Bar, serves Mediterranean cuisine, both for lunch and dinner. It is also possible to taste an aperitif.\nThe Hotel also has 4 fully equipped meeting rooms and private parking, as well as free Wi-Fi in rooms and common areas.", 'It is about 20 minutes away by car from Barcelona airport and 10 from the AVE station.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at The Mirror Barcelona! name: Acta Atrium Palace
address: Gran Via Corts Catalanes, 656, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This elegant hotel is 250 m from Paseo de Gracia Metro Station and Boulevard. Plaza Catalunya is a 5-minute walk away. It offers free Wi-Fi.', 'Set in an attractive building, dating from 1888, rooms at the Acta Atrium Palace are modern and chic, with air conditioning and satellite TV. The private bathrooms offer free toiletries and a bathrobe.', 'The hotel has 24-hour room service.', "Gaudí's famous Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are 10 minutes' walk away. There is a 24-hour front desk, and you can hire a car at the hotel tour desk. Public parking is available nearby."]

name: Hilton Barcelona
address: Avenida Diagonal, 589 - 591, Les Corts, 08014 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Featuring an impressive lobby, the stylish Hilton Barcelona offers free WiFi, access to its 24-hour gym and rooms with city views and plasma TV. The hotel is a 15-minute walk from FC Barcelona’s Camp Nou Stadium.', 'Each stylish, soundproofed room at the Barcelona Hilton features air conditioning, iPod docking stations and tea and coffee-making facilities.', 'Hotel Hilton Barcelona is just 100 m from L’Illa Shopping Center and 300 m from María Cristina Metro Station. Plaça Catalunya and the historic city center are 15 minutes away by Metro. You can drive to Sants Station in 5 minutes, and El Prat Airport is a 15-minute drive away.', 'Hilton Barcelona’s Mosaic restaurant offers Catalan and Mediterranean cuisine prepared using seasonal, local products. The Vibe Bar & Restaurant serves tapas and cocktails. Guests can enjoy live sport on the bar’s large TV.']

name: Park Hotel
address: Avenida Marques de Argentera, 11, Ciutat Vella, 08003 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Park Hotel! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", "Located in Barcelona’s trendy Born district, Park Hotel offers stylish accommodations just 10 minutes' walk from Barceloneta Beach, opposite to Estació de França Station. Reception is open 24 hours a day. Free WiFi is offered throughout the property.", 'The air-conditioned rooms at the Hotel Park feature modern décor in warm tones. They are equipped with flat-screen satellite TV, and soundproofing.', "A buffet breakfast is served daily in the hotel’s bright café; and a wide variety of tapas are served at the on-site Ten's Tapas Restaurant, from the awarded-winning chef Jordi Cruz.", 'Park Hotel is just 200 m from Mercat del Born public market and from Ciudadela Park, where you can find Barcelona Zoo.', 'Barceloneta Metro Station, located 300 m from the hotel, connects you with the city center in just 5 minutes.']

name: Nobu Hotel Barcelona
address: Avenida de Roma, 4, Sants-Montjuïc, 08014 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in Barcelona, a 4-minute walk from Sants Railway Station, Nobu Hotel Barcelona has air-conditioned accommodations and a bar. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. Private parking is available on site.', 'All guest rooms in the hotel are equipped with a coffee machine. The rooms have a safety deposit box.', 'Guests at Nobu Hotel Barcelona can enjoy a à la carte breakfast.', 'Magic Fountain of Montjuic is a 16-minute walk from the accommodation, while Casa Batllo is 2.7 km from the property. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 14 km from Nobu Hotel Barcelona.']

name: Olivia Balmes Hotel
address: Balmes, 117, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Featuring an outdoor swimming pool, Olivia Balmes Hotel is a quarter mile from Barcelona’s Passeig de Gracia, in the elegant Eixample neighborhood. The modern hotel features stylish air-conditioned rooms and a restaurant.', 'Each bright spacious room includes free Wi-Fi, a flat-screen satellite TV and a laptop safe. The contemporary bathrooms have an open-plan design.', 'The hotel’s restaurant serves breakfast, lunch and dinner. Olivia Balmes has a terrace with an outdoor swimming pool and lounge chairs. There is also a bar, serving cocktails and snacks, as well as several meeting rooms.', 'Olivia Balmes Hotel has private parking, and Barcelona Airport is around a 20-minute drive from the hotel. Plaza Catalunya is a 15-minute walk from the hotel, and Gaudi’s famous Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are within a 5-minute walk of the hotel.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Expo Hotel Barcelona! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Hotel Expo Barcelona is located next to Barcelona Sants Station. Its rooftop pool and terrace offer fantastic city views and the modern rooms feature a private balcony and satellite TV.', 'The hotel’s stylish Stop’n’Bite restaurant serves international à la carte food. There is also a terrace bar in the rooftop chillout area, which provides views over Barcelona.', 'The Expo Hotel has 24-hour reception, allowing you greater flexibility during your stay. Bicycle hire is available to enjoy the city.', 'Montjuïc Hill, where you can find the Joan Miró Museum and Barcelona’s Fira Congress Center, is 10 minutes’ walk away. Barcelona FC’s Camp Nou Stadium is just one metro stop away.']

name: Catalonia Port
address: Ample, 1 (Plaça Duc de Medinaceli), Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Port! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located in Barcelona’s Gothic Quarter, Hotel Catalonia Port has a modern gym and a sun terrace with a small seasonal outdoor pool. Each air-conditioned room has free WiFi, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels.', 'The hotel’s contemporary El Racó del Port restaurant opens from Monday to Saturday, serving seasonal Mediterranean cuisine. A varied buffet breakfast, available until 12:00 at the weekends, is offered in the dining room, and there is also a lobby bar.', 'The Catalonia Port Hotel offers stylish rooms with hardwood floors. They all include a safe, a mini-bar and a private bathroom.', 'Catalonia Port is just 250 m from the bottom of the famous Las Ramblas, and Port Vell Harbor is 400 m away. Drassanes Metro Station is a 5-minute walk away.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel Best Auto Hogar! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set on Parallel Avenue, the Hotel Auto Hogar is right across from Parallel Metro Station and a 10-minute walk from the Ramblas. It includes air-conditioned rooms with private bathrooms.', 'All rooms have a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. The private bathroom includes a hairdryer and vanity mirror.', 'Some of Barcelona’s most popular theaters can be found within a 5-minute walk, and Montjuïc hill is a 15-minute walk from the hotel. The Fira Exhibition Centre is just over half a kilometer away.', 'The Auto Hogar Hotel’s restaurant serves Mediterranean dishes, and is open 7 days a week. The hotel also has a café.', 'The hotel front desk provides free newspapers, and can arrange bike and car rental.']

hotel_description: ['Located in Barcelona, 0.9 mi from Sagrada Familia, Golden Hotel Barcelona is a sustainable property with the Biosphere certificate. name: Catalonia Ramblas 4* Sup
address: Pelai, 28, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Ramblas 4* Sup! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set just off Barcelona’s famous Las Ramblas, 3 minutes’ walk from central Plaza Catalunya, Catalonia Ramblas 4* Sup features a seasonal outdoor pool with a south-facing terrace, a poolside snack bar and a chill-out area.', 'Housed in a modernist building, all bright and spacious rooms come with a flat-screen satellite TV, free WiFi and tea and coffee facilities. Some have a private terrace with a private pool. Room service is available.', 'The spa at Catalonia Ramblas 4* Sup features a relaxation area. It includes a sauna, a steam bath and a hot tub. Massage and beauty treatments are also available.', 'The hotel’s restaurant, Pelai Restaurant, offers Catalan market cuisine. Dishes cooked on a coal stove are available at the Pelai terrace, a rooftop terrace with a chill-out area with panoramic city views. A buffet breakfast is offered every morning and, on weekends, it is available until 12:00.', 'In the summer months, the terrace is open until 00:00 and has a summer menu, as well as cocktails and milkshakes.']

name: Hotel Acta Azul Barcelona
address: Gran Via de Les Corts Catalanes, 327, Sants-Montjuïc, 08014 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Set just off Plaça d’Espanya and at the foot of Montjuïc, Hotel Acta Azul Barcelona offers stylish accommodations in central Barcelona. It features a roof terrace, 24-hour reception and free Wi-Fi.', 'Las Ramblas and the city’s Gothic Quarter can be reached in less than 10 minutes, by Metro and here you will find where a selection of bars and restaurants.', 'Each of the Azul’s spacious rooms has bright décor and wooden flooring. All rooms have air conditioning, satellite TV and a desk.', 'The hotel is a 5-minute walk from Barcelona’s Fira Conference Center and Plaça d’Espanya’s Magic Fountains. Montjuïc Park and the MNAC Gallery are within 0.6 mi of the hotel. The bullring-turned-shopping center of Las Arenas is next door.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel Royal Passeig de Gracia! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Within 50 m of La Pedrera and Diagonal Metro Station, Hotel Royal Passeig de Gracia features a terrace bar with panoramic views of Barcelona. This 4-star hotel also has an interior garden.', 'Hotel Royal Passeig de Gracia is set in a restored building with contemporary architecture. The smart bedrooms come with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, free Wi-Fi and a bathroom with a rain-effect shower.', 'Casa Batlló is just 5 minutes’ walk from the hotel, while Plaza Catalunya and Las Ramblas are 2 stops from Diagonal Station.', 'The Gràcia district is within a 5-minute walk, and charming street cafés can be found along the tree-lined Rambla de Catalunya, 200 m away.']

name: Room Mate Anna
address: Carrer de Aragó, 271, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Room Mate Anna! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Featuring a seasonal rooftop plunge pool with views and a solarium, Room Mate Anna is set in Barcelona City Center. The hotel features cutting-edge and modern design as well as personalized service. The hotel serves a daily hot and cold buffet breakfast until midday.', 'Each stylish, air-conditioned room comes with free WiFi and a flat-screen TV. Some rooms have a seating area to relax in after a busy day as well as a balcony with views over Casa Batlló. Extras include a wide variety of free toiletries, a hairdryer and safe box.', 'Other facilities include a portable WiFi and meeting and conference rooms.', 'On the eigth floor of the hotel the bar Terraza de Anna by Vida Mona offers views over the city, cocktails and mediterranean tapas.\nThe restaurant Vibra Speakeasy, inspired by the style of 1920, offers live music, food and cocktails from that time.', "The Room Mate Anna is set in the heart of L'Eixample, just 100 m from Casa Batlló. You will find a wide range of shops, restaurants, and cultural spots. Barcelona El Prat Airport is 8.1 mi from the property."]

name: Room Mate Carla
address: Mallorca, 288, Eixample, 08037 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Room Mate Carla! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Room Mate Carla is set 200 m from Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard, and 5-minutes’ walk from Gaudí’s La Pedrera in Barcelona’s Eixample District. It features free WiFi and colorful, stylish rooms.', 'Decorated with lively prints, the air-conditioned rooms include a flat-screen TV, mini-bar, safe and a private bathroom.', 'Room Mate Carla features a modern bar offering a range of cocktails. You will also find a terrace and meeting rooms on site.', 'The hotel is a 15-minute walk from the Sagrada Familia Cathedral. Verdaguer and Diagonal Metro Stations are 500 m away and offer easy access to Las Ramblas and Sants Train Station.']

It has an 8th-floor swimming pool and sun terrace with spectacular views of Montjuic.', 'The air-conditioned rooms at B Hotel are spacious and soundproofed. All rooms have free WiFi, and are decorated with contemporary art. Each room comes with an electric kettle and a pillow-menu.', 'The room service menu is also available at the bar and by the swimming pool.', 'Plaza Espanya Metro Station is within 200 m of the hotel, while Barcelona Fira Exhibition Center is just 250 m away. The Magic Fountains of Montjuic are about 5 minutes’ walk away.']

name: Leonardo Hotel Barcelona Las Ramblas
address: Junta de Comercio, 8,10,12, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Leonardo Hotel Barcelona Las Ramblas is located in the center of Barcelona’s Old Town, just 200 m from Las Ramblas. It features a rooftop terrace with a seasonal swimming pool.', 'The hotel offers simple, attractive décor and rooms are spacious. Each has air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, as well as tea and coffee making facilities.', 'The Leonardo Hotel Barcelona Las Ramblas serves a daily, buffet breakfast. There are several bars, cafés and restaurants within walking distance of the property.', 'Guests can make use of computers with internet access, available in the hotel reception area. Staff at the tour desk can provide information on Barcelona’s tourist attractions and arrange car rental.', 'The hotel is 10 minutes’ walk from Barcelona Cathedral and the city’s Gothic Quarter. The Old Port is around 701 m from the hotel, while Liceu Metro is a 10-minute walk away.']

name: Duquesa de Cardona 4* Sup
address: Passeig Colom, 12, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['The 19th-century Duquesa de Cardona, opposite Barcelona’s marina in the Gothic Quarter, is 601 m from the Ramblas and has free Wi-Fi. Its rooftop terrace offers panoramic city views and includes 2 plunge pools and a bar. Property also features a Gym.', 'Duquesa de Cardona Hotel Barcelona has spacious, air-conditioned rooms with a flat-screen satellite TV, a safety deposit box and a mini-bar. The private bathroom comes with a bathrobe and slippers.', 'The hotel’s restaurant offers Mediterranean cuisine and has an extensive wine list, including many Spanish cavas. During summer, the snack bar serves creative tapas, BBQ dishes and cocktails.', 'The famous Sagrada Familia is 1.6 mi away, and Barceloneta Metro Station is only 300 m away. The Maremagnum Shopping Center and Barcelona Aquarium are 500 m from Duquesa de Cardona Barcelona.']

name: Leonardo Boutique Hotel Barcelona Sagrada Familia
address: Mallorca, 606, Sant Martí, 08026 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Leonardo Boutique Hotel Barcelona Sagrada Familia is located just 15 minutes’ walk from Gaudí’s famous Sagrada Familia. It has a rooftop sun terrace with panoramic views of Barcelona and rooms with free Wi-Fi.', 'All modern, outward-facing rooms at theLeonardo Boutique Hotel Barcelona Sagrada Familia are equipped with air conditioning and heating. They have a flat-screen TV and the private bathrooms come with a hairdryer.', 'Leonardo Boutique Hotel Barcelona Sagrada Familia serves a daily buffet breakfast, and gluten-free meals are available on prior request. In summer, breakfast can be enjoyed on the terrace. There are also vending machines with snacks and drinks.', 'Staff at the hotel’s 24-hour reception can provide information about what to see and do in Barcelona. Clot Metro Station is 200 m away, allowing you to reach the city center in 10 minutes.']

name: Axel Hotel Barcelona & Urban Spa- Adults Only
address: Aribau, 33, Eixample, 08011 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['The area around the Hotel Axel Barcelona is known as the Gay-xample because of its lively gay scene. The staff has knowledge of the local gay scene, and the hotel is hetero-friendly too.', "Offering free Wi-Fi throughout, this design hotel is close to Passeig de Gràcia's exclusive boutiques. The Axel Hotel’s 1640 ft² Spa Center includes a hydromassage pool and saunas, and the modern rooms have flat-screen satellite TVs.", 'The Axel’s Sky Bar features a large swimming pool, a terrace with a hot tub and a cocktail bar. Here you will find parties, art exhibitions and shows.', 'The Axel Hotel Barcelona & Urban Spa offers easy access to the Ramblas, the Picasso Museum and Gothic Quarter. The hotel occupies an attractive 19th-century building.']

name: Catalonia Eixample 1864
address: Roger de Llúria, 60, Eixample, 08009 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Eixample 1864! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located in Barcelona’s Eixample district, this 19th-century building offers stylish modern interiors and free WiFi. It is just 300 m from the designer shops and Gaudí buildings of Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard.', 'The Catalonia Eixample 1864 is housed in one of the Eixample’s oldest buildings, and its painted façade gives it the Specialty Monument status.', 'All soundproofed rooms with attached bathroom sleek wooden floors and furniture, air conditioning and satellite TV. Some rooms have a private terrace and pool.', "A buffet breakfast with show cooking is offered every morning at the Sala Minerva; while the hotel's Les Finestres de Llúria restaurant serves traditional Catalan food with a creative twist. Room service is also available.", 'Catalonia Eixample 1864 features a rooftop swimming pool, sundeck and bar; as well as a gym.', 'The Catalonia Eixample 1864 is ideally located just a 5-minute walk from Passeig de Gracia Station. Plaza Catalunya Square is a 10-minute walk away.', 'The hotel offers private parking on-site for an extra cost and an electric vehicle charging station.']

name: Catalonia Gracia
address: Córcega, 368, Eixample, 08037 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Gracia! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'This hotel is located next to Avinguda Diagonal and Passeig de Gràcia, ideal for shopping. Guests can easily access Plaza Cataluña and the city’s historic gothic quarter. Free Wi-Fi is available.', "Located along the modernist route, Hotel Catalonia Gracia is surrounded by much of the interesting architecture that Barcelona is famous for, such as Gaudí and Domenech i Muntaner's key buildings, including La Pedrera.", 'A buffet breakfast is available at the on-site restaurant; room service is also available.', 'Guests can easily enjoy this cosmopolitan city as Hotel Catalonia Gracia is within walking distance of Barcelona’s many attractions. As well as the excellent public transport links providing swift access to the entire city and the surrounding area, the hotel offers great value for money. The hotel also includes meeting amenities and conference rooms available for business events and banquets.']

name: Hotel Concordia Barcelona
address: Paral·lel, 115, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hotel Concordia Barcelona is located 801 m from Plaza España and the Fira de Barcelona Exhibition Center. It features a sun terrace with an outdoor swimming pool, hot tub, cocktail bar and solarium.', 'The Hotel Concordia Barcelona’s bright, spacious rooms feature contemporary décor and air conditioning. Each room includes free WiFi, a flat-screen TV, safe, mini-bar and a private bathroom with a range of amenities.', 'The Concordia Barcelona’s modern, elegant Bistro Triple Sec Restaurant serves characteristic Mediterranean cuisine. The varied breakfast buffet includes healthy options. There is also a café and cocktail bar open daily. Private parking is available on site for an extra cost and electrical cars charging station is available.', 'Located next to Poble Sec Station, the hotel is a 5-minute Metro journey from Barcelona Port and La Rambla. You can also walk to the Rambla in 15 minutes. Direct airport busses stop in Plaza España, a 15-minute walk away.', 'Private parking is available on site for an extra cost.']

name: The Moods Oasis
address: 72 Travessera de Gràcia, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08006 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Ideally located in the Sarrià-St. Gervasi district of Barcelona, The Moods Oasis is located a 12-minute walk from La Pedrera, 1.4 km from Casa Batllo and 1.9 km from Passeig de Gracia. This 3-star hotel offers a concierge service and a tour desk. The hotel has a fitness center, a 24-hour front desk and free WiFi throughout the property.', 'The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower. At The Moods Oasis the rooms have bed linen and towels.', 'Guests at the accommodation can enjoy a continental or a buffet breakfast.', 'The Moods Oasis has a terrace.', 'The hotel provides an ironing service, as well as business facilities like fax and photocopying.', 'Passeig de Gracia Metro Station is 1.8 km from The Moods Oasis, while Plaça Catalunya is 2.1 km from the property. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 16.1 km from the accommodation.']

name: AinB Eixample-Miro Apartments
address: Entença, 140, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at AinB Eixample-Miro Apartments! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'These stylish and comfortable apartments are in Barcelona’s chic Eixample district, just over a quarter mile from Gran Vía. They feature a balcony, air conditioning and free Wi-Fi, a 10-minute walk from Plaza España.', 'Apartments in Barcelona Eixample-Miro have chic decor and plenty of natural light. Lounges have a sofa bed and plasma TV and modern kitchens include a coffee machine, microwave, stove and oven.', 'There are various bars, restaurants and shops within a 5-minute walk of the property. The Las Arenas Shopping Center is a 10-minute walk away.', 'The foot of Montjuic hill, with the Olympic Stadium, MNAC and Caixa Forum Museums, is a 10-minute walk away and the Joan Miró Park is a 4-minute walk away.', 'The Eixample-Miro apartments are a 5-minute walk from Entença and Tarragona Metro Stations, connecting you with Las Ramblas in 10 minutes. Sants AVE Train Station is less than half a kilometer away.']

address: Boqueria, 23, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel Condal! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set 50 m from Las Ramblas and Liceu Metro Station, Hotel Condal offers rooms with free WiFi and private bathrooms. Opened in 1850, this hotel in Barcelona’s Gothic Quarter offers air conditioned or heated accommodations, depending on the season.', 'The Condal’s rooms have simple décor with tiled floors. Each room has a flat-screen TV.', 'A continental breakfast is served in Hotel Condal’s café-bar. The Condal is less than 0.6 mi from Port Vell Marina.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Europark! name: Zenit Borrell
address: Comte Borrell, 208, Eixample, 08029 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Zenit Borrell is in Barcelona’s Eixample district, a 15 minute walk from the stylish Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard. It offers modern, soundproof rooms with free Wi-Fi and satellite TV.', 'The Marés restaurant offers Mediterranean and international cuisine, and has an elegant outdoor terrace. There is also a bar with a large TV screen.', 'All rooms at the Zenit Borrell have air conditioning and a minibar. The private bathrooms come equipped with a hairdryer.', 'The tour desk can provide useful information on Barcelona and the surrounding area. The hotel is 12 minutes from Plaza Catalunya and the Ramblas by metro, while the Hospital Clinic Metro Station and hospital are 202 m away from the hotel.']

hotel_description: ['AC Hotel Barcelona Forum is located opposite Diagonal Mar Shopping Center, at the end of Avenida Diagonal. It offers a rooftop pool and modern rooms with Mediterranean Sea views. name: Hotel Balmes
address: Mallorca, 216, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Balmes is located in central Barcelona, 5 minutes’ walk from the famous Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard. It offers a swimming pool, a gym/fitness center and modern rooms with satellite TV.', 'The air-conditioned rooms at Hotel Balmes feature parquet floors and smart, simple décor. They all come with a private bathroom, a flat-screen TV and free Wi-Fi.', 'The hotel’s restaurant serves characteristic Catalan food using fresh market produce. B Bar, like the rest of the hotel, is decorated with works of African art.', 'Staff at the hotel’s 24-hour reception can help booking tickets for guided tours, live shows and other events. There is a computer in the lobby which guests can use for free.', 'Gaudí’s Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are both under 10 minutes’ walk from the hotel. You can walk to Las Ramblas and Barcelona’s charming Gothic Quarter in around 15 minutes.']

name: Catalonia Passeig de Gràcia 4* Sup
address: Gran Via de les Corts Catalanes, 644, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Passeig de Gràcia 4* Sup! hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel SOFIA Barcelona, in The Unbound Collection by Hyatt! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", "Hotel Sofia Barcelona is set on Barcelona's Diagonal Avenue, a 5-minute walk from FC Barcelona’s Camp Nou Stadium. It features free WiFi throughout, on-site restaurants and stunning city views. Guests have free access to a bright, modern 24-hour gym with a variety of equipment.", 'Designer rooms at Sofia offer home automation technology, a 49-inch Smart TV, a safe, and air conditioning. Their private bathroom includes Natura Bissé amenities, bathrobes and slippers.', 'The hotel offers several gastronomic spaces, including SOFIA Be So restaurant serving traditional dishes, and Impar Restaurant, which serves fresh Mediterranean dishes prepared with international culinary techniques. It also features a spacious outdoor terrace.', 'Guests will also find a sophisticated book cafe, Philosofia, which serves confectionery and fresh pastries, to eat in or take away.', 'Sofia Oasis Wellness & Spa houses more than 3281 ft² space for well-being, including water circuits, saunas and steam baths. You can relax with one of the range of treatments available onsite and coordinated by expert therapists.', 'Sofia Barcelona, in The Unbound Collection by Hyatt is 400 m from Maria Cristina Metro Station and the central Plaza España Square is 3 metro stops away. L’Illa Diagonal Shopping Center is 15 minutes away on foot.']

name: Vincci Gala
address: Ronda Sant Pere, 32, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Vincci Gala! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'In the heart of Barcelona, Vincci Gala hotel offers luxurious rooms in a protected 19th-century palace. Free Wi-Fi is available.', 'The orginal façade, floor and central staircase of this unique hotel have all been preserved, creating a balance of traditional arquitecture and modern design.', 'The air-conditioned rooms include a private bathroom with hairdryer, free toiletries, and bathtub or shower. The rooms also have a free laptop safe, extra large beds, satellite TV with pay-per-view channels, and a minibar.', 'A restaurant and snack bar are available on-site, and the hotel offers a breakfast buffet. Laundry and car rental services are available for a fee, and the property can provide tourist information.', "Vincci Gala hotel is located across from Urquinaona Metro Station, a 2-minute walk from Plaça Catalunya Square. There are many bars, restaurants and shops in the surroundings, and you can reach Gaudi's La Sagrada Familia in 15 minutes by metro."]

name: Royal Ramblas
address: Las Ramblas, 117, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Royal Ramblas! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", "Royal Ramblas is located on Barcelona's famous Ramblas, 100 m from Plaza de Catalunya. It offers elegant and modern rooms with air conditioning, plasma TV, free Wi-Fi, and private parking. Some rooms provide magnificent views of the Ramblas.", 'The Hotel has a meeting room with magnificent views of the Ramblas.', 'It offers a buffet breakfast with various regional products and homemade pastries in the La Poma restaurant with impressive views of Las Ramblas where you can also taste Mediterranean food.', 'The Royal Ramblas Hotel is ideally located with access to all public transport and a 5-minute walk from the elegant Passeig de Gràcia, where you will find numerous restaurants and exclusive shops. The old town is within walking distance, as well as the Mercat de la Boqueria and the MACBA. The beach is 20 minutes away.', "The Royal Ramblas Barcelona's tour desk offers useful information about the city and car rental services. It also manages the airport transfer service."]

name: MH Apartments Suites
address: Girona, 110, Eixample, 08009 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at MH Apartments Suites! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'MH Apartments Suites is located in Barcelona’s Eixample district, 519 m from the prestigious Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard. It offers modern apartments with free Wi-Fi and international satellite TV.', 'The modern MH Suites feature stylish décor and parquet floors. They all have a sitting area with sofas, a flat-screen TV and DVD player.', 'The kitchens at MH Apartments feature an oven, stove and Nespresso coffee maker. There is also a washing machine.', 'Late check-out is available upon request at MH Apartments Suites. There is 24-hour customer service, and check-in staff can provide information about what to see and do in Barcelona.', 'Gaudí’s La Pedrera and Casa Batlló are under a 10 minute walk from the apartments. Girona and Verdaguer Metro Stations are both a 5-minute walk away, providing easy access to the rest of the city.']

name: El Avenida Palace
address: Gran Via, 605, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['El Avenida Palace Hotel is set on Barcelona’s Gran Via, 5 minutes’ walk from Plaza Catalunya, La Rambla and Paseo de Gracia. Its grand interior features an impressive staircase and marble columns.', 'Many famous guests have stayed at the Hotel Avenida Palace, including the Beatles in 1965.', 'The elegant air-conditioned rooms feature satellite TV and carpeted or parquet floors. Rooms are soundproofed and have a mini-bar, work desk and a safe.', "The hotel's panoramic rooftop terrace offers views over the city, a sun deck and a swimming pool. There is also a lounge bar, a 24-hour front desk and both free WiFi and room service are available."]

name: Hotel Granados 83, a Member of Design Hotels
address: Enrique Granados, 83, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located 250 m from Barcelona’s Diagonal Metro Station, Granados 83 offers a small gym and roof terrace with a small pool and cocktail bar. Rooms feature Zen-style design and LCD TV.', 'This design hotel has an impressive glass and stone façade and it combines neoclassical details with industrial and natural components which has become representative of the entire city and which gives it the Specialty Monument status. It also features beautiful Art Deco interiors.', 'Decorated with wood, leather and glass, the Granados 83’s stylish air-conditioned rooms include a mini-bar, bathrobe and slippers.', 'The elegant restaurant serves creative Mediterranean cuisine and room service is available. There are many popular tapas bars within a 5-minute walk, on Rambla de Catalunya.', 'Passeig de Gràcia is 400 m away, and is home to Gaudí’s famous La Pedrera and Casa Batlló.', 'There is a 24-hour reception and free Wi-Fi throughout the hotel. You can hire a car from the tour desk, and on-site parking is offered for an extra charge.']

hotel_description: ['Zenit Barcelona is 250 m from Plaza Francesc Macià on Barcelona’s Diagonal Avenue. address: 5 Carrer de Magalhães 2º 2ª, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Featuring a balcony with city views, an outdoor swimming pool and a fitness center, Brummell Apartments Montjuic can be found in Barcelona, close to Magic Fountain of Montjuic and 2.9 km from Santa Maria del Mar. Guests might go for a swim in the private pool and enjoy the free WiFi.', 'This air-conditioned apartment comes with 2 bedrooms, a satellite flat-screen TV, a dining area, and a kitchen with a dishwasher and a microwave. Towels and bed linen are featured.', 'The apartment offers a sauna. A sun terrace is available for guests to use at Brummell Apartments Montjuic.', "Popular points of interest near the accommodation include Boqueria Market, Montjuïc and Portal de l'Angel. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 16.1 km from Brummell Apartments Montjuic."]

address: Rec Comtal, 16-18, Ciutat Vella, 08003 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Born! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set in a 19th-century building in Barcelona’s El Born district, Catalonia Born offers a rooftop pool, an attractive central courtyard and free Wi-Fi. Arc de Triomf Metro Station is 250 m away.', 'The classic rooms at Catalonia Born Hotel come with an elegant marble bathroom. They also include a satellite TV and centrally controlled heating or air conditioning, depending on the season.', 'A buffet breakfast is served, and the snack bar is open for lunch and dinner. There is also a bar in the lobby.', 'Located minutes from França Train Station, the hotel is well-connected to the rest of the city and its surroundings. Car rental is also available from the tour desk.']

name: Unkown122
address: Avenida Rius y Taulet, 1-3, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located 200 m from Barcelona’s Magic Fountain, the elegant InterContinental Barcelona, an IHG Hotel offers spacious rooms with a flat-screen TV and hydromassage shower.', 'Offering fantastic views over Barcelona, the hotel’s 173 Rooftop Terrace features an outdoor pool, sun loungers, and a dining area where guests can enjoy Mediterranean cuisine and a selection of drinks and cocktails.', 'Arrel Restaurant pays homage to the land and the produce it provides throughout all seasons of the year. The restaurant features an open kitchen serving small portions to share, buffet breakfasts and lunch and dinner service.', 'Quirat Restaurant is an exclusive space that will offer an interpretation of the land and its products through a menu of dishes that responds to the different seasons, designed exclusively for the restaurant by a Chef with 1 Michelin Star. Enjoy an unforgettable dinner in the most exclusive of our restaurants.', 'Gebre Cocktails and More and, in addition to the cocktail classics, it will offer a menu of artisan signature cocktails that will try to convey a very specific sensory experience connected to the world of the land that surrounds us.', 'There is free WiFi available in public areas and in rooms and the lobby area at InterContinental Barcelona, an IHG Hotel features a free internet point.', 'The spa has a water circuit, a dry sauna, a hammam, hot tub, gym, and 6 treatment cabins.', 'From the hotel, Barcelona’s historic center can be easily reached by bus or metro. Poble Sec and Espanya Metro Stations are both 500 m away. Poble Espanyol and the Joan Miró Foundation are 200 m away.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Ilunion Les Corts Spa! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'The Ilunion Les Corts Spa is 500 m from Barcelona FC’s Nou Camp Stadium. The rooftop pool has views of the city and is open in summer. Free Wi-Fi is available.', "The hotel's spa offers a range of facilities including Turkish baths, hot tubs, Roman and Indian baths, ice caves and sauna, all available for an extra charge. Different types of massages and beauty treatments are available as well. Check prices with hotel.", 'The Ilunion Les Corts Spa offers 2 bottles of complementary water. There is soundproofing and a free safe.', "The hotel's restaurant serves a varied buffet breakfast, and show cooking. There is also a bar where guests can relax with a drink.", 'Collblanc Metro Station is within 701 m. This offers direct access to the Airport (20min), Europa/Fira, Sagrada Familia and the main train station of Sants. The city center is 15 minutes away.', 'Pets allowed, dogs only, under availability with the hotel. Supplements per night apply. Guests should contact the hotel to check and confirm availability of this room type. Once at the property, guests will receive the rules of access, which must be read and approved.']

name: Barceló Sants
address: Plaza Paisos Catalans, s/n, Sants-Montjuïc, 08014 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Barceló Sants! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located above Barcelona Sants Train Station, Barceló Sants offers a subtle outer space theme throughout. Minimalist rooms feature free Wi-Fi, rain showers, and large windows with city views.', 'Air-conditioned rooms feature modern décor and designer furniture. Each has an iPod dock, flat-screen TV, and tea and coffee making facilities. The bathroom comes with a hairdryer.', 'This design hotel includes a fitness center.', "The hotel has 2 restaurants. Oxygen Restaurant serves a healthy buffet and Hydrogen Restaurant offers more avant-garde cuisine. The hotel's Orbital Bar serves a selection of cocktails, gins and vodkas. You can also try characteristic tapas in the many nearby bars and restaurants.", 'Sants Train and Metro Station offers direct access to Barcelona Airport, and the historic city center, 2.2 mi away. There are also high-speed AVE services to Madrid and international trains.', 'There is a 24-hour front desk, and you can hire a car from the tour desk. On-site parking is available for an extra charge and the hotel has a Wi-Fi zone.']

name: Catalonia Roma
address: Avenida Roma, 31, Eixample, 08029 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Roma! Room service is available and there is also a bar.', 'Plaza Espanya, Montjuic’s Magic Fountain and the Fira Conference Center are all within 15 minutes’ walk of the hotel.', 'The 24-hour front desk at Catalonia Roma features a large stained-glass skylight.
