name: Catalonia Catedral
address: Arcs, 10, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Catedral! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'The Catalonia Catedral is set in a traditional Modernist building, just 100 m from Barcelona Cathedral. It offers free use of Smartphones, Wi-Fi access, a rooftop seasonal pool and a Japanese-style terrace and garden.', 'The Catedral has stylish rooms, which have contemporary décor. Each has a flat-screen TV, air conditioning, a mini-bar, a Nespresso machine. A smartphone is available for guests during their stay free of charge.', 'The hotel’s Ascent Restaurant by Eboca serves Mediterrean cuisine and offers views of the nearby Palacio Pignatelli Art Gallery. There is also a bar in the hotel lobby where guests can use the computers with internet access and printers for free.', "The Catalonia Catedral is around 10 minutes’ walk from landmarks such as Las Ramblas and Plaza de Catalunya Square. Barcelona’s Old Port and Marina are less than one kilometer away. Jaume I Metro Station is 5 minutes' walk away."]

name: Vincci Bit
address: Josep Pla, 69, Sant Martí, 08019 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Vincci Bit! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Vincci Bit is a modern, stylish hotel located just 10 minutes’ walk from Mar Bella beach. Located a 7-minute walk from El Maresme Forum Metro Station, it features a sauna, a gym and a rooftop swimming pool (measures 7 m. x 2.7 m. Depth 1 m) with views over the city.', 'This stylish hotel has a dynamic feel and each floor features a unique design from such graffiti artists as Alex Trochut, Matthey More, and Lorenzo Petrantoni. Its contemporary restaurant serves a buffet breakfast and à la carte meals, and the breakfast includes gluten-free products. There is also a lounge, bar and room service available.', 'The air-conditioned rooms at Vincci Bit are bright and comfortable and feature a flat-screen TV, a pillow menu and a mini-bar. The private bathrooms include a shower, hairdryer and free toiletries. Free Wi-Fi is also available.', 'There are a number of bars, restaurants and shops within a few minutes’ walk from the hotel. Diagonal Mar Shopping Center is just 300 m away.', 'The International Convention Center (CCIB) is a 9-minute walk from Vincci Bit. The historic center of Barcelona can be reached in just 15-minutes by metro or tram.']

name: Ayre Hotel Gran Vía
address: Gran Vía de les Corts Catalanes 322, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Ayre Hotel Gran Vía! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'The Ayre Hotel Gran Via is a modern design hotel with a bright central courtyard. It offers free Wi-Fi and a convenient location, next to Barcelona’s Plaça Espanya.', 'The modern rooms at the Ayre Hotel Barcelona feature a private bathroom, and free mineral water for the first night. They are all soundproofed, with flat-screen TVs and air conditioning.', 'The Ayre Gran Vía is set next to the Fira Exhibition Center, at the bottom of Montjuic. This hill is home to a castle, the National Art Museum and the Magic Fountain.', 'Espanya Metro Station is 150 m from the hotel. The historic center of Barcelona and the famous Ramblas are just a few stops away. A direct bus service to the airport stops in Plaça Espanya, near the hotel.', 'Breakfast is available at an additional cost.']

name: Barceló Sants
address: Plaza Paisos Catalans, s/n, Sants-Montjuïc, 08014 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Barceló Sants! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located above Barcelona Sants Train Station, Barceló Sants offers a subtle outer space theme throughout. Minimalist rooms feature free Wi-Fi, rain showers, and large windows with city views.', 'Air-conditioned rooms feature modern décor and designer furniture. Each has an iPod dock, flat-screen TV, and tea and coffee making facilities. The bathroom comes with a hairdryer.', 'This design hotel includes a fitness center.', "The hotel has 2 restaurants. Oxygen Restaurant serves a healthy buffet and Hydrogen Restaurant offers more avant-garde cuisine. The hotel's Orbital Bar serves a selection of cocktails, gins and vodkas. You can also try characteristic tapas in the many nearby bars and restaurants.", 'Sants Train and Metro Station offers direct access to Barcelona Airport, and the historic city center, 2.2 mi away. There are also high-speed AVE services to Madrid and international trains.', 'There is a 24-hour front desk, and you can hire a car from the tour desk. On-site parking is available for an extra charge and the hotel has a Wi-Fi zone.']

To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Casual Colors Barcelona is set approximately 10 minutes’ walk from Barcelona Sants Railway Station and 200 m from Avinguda Diagonal. The airport bus also stops here.']

address: 344 Carrer de Còrsega, Eixample, 08037 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Seventy Barcelona! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located in Barcelona and with La Pedrera reachable within a 4-minute walk, Seventy Barcelona has concierge services, allergy-free rooms, a bar, free WiFi throughout the property and a shared lounge. This 4-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and room service. The property has a year-round outdoor pool, indoor pool, fitness center and restaurant.', 'At the hotel the rooms have air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a shower, bathrobes and slippers. Seventy Barcelona provides some accommodations that have a terrace, and every room is equipped with an electric tea pot. At the accommodation rooms are equipped with bed linen and towels.', 'Guests at Seventy Barcelona can enjoy a continental or a buffet breakfast.', 'The hotel offers guests a spa and wellness center with a hammam and a sauna.', 'Popular points of interest near Seventy Barcelona include Casa Batllo, Passeig de Gracia and Passeig de Gracia Metro Station. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 16.1 km from the accommodation.']

name: MH Apartments Ramblas
address: Nou de la Rambla, 20, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at MH Apartments Ramblas! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'MH Apartments Ramblas is located in front of Palau Güell, 121 m from Las Ramblas of Barcelona. Columbus Monument and Moll de Barcelona Ferry Station are within 10 minutes’ walk away.', 'Each bright and air-conditioned apartment features city views. There is a living room with a TV, CD and DVD player, a dining area and a well-equipped kitchen. There is free high-speed WiFi.', 'The apartments at MH also include a washing machine and basic cleaning products. Tourist information can be provided at the reception.', 'The nearest metro station is Liceu, which is 350 m away from MH Apartments Ramblas. Plaça Catalunya Square is 0.6 mi away.']

name: Paral·lel
address: Poeta Cabanyes, 5, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Paral·lel! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Situated just a 10-minutes walk from the stunning center of Barcelona, this stylish and practical hotel is set in the charming neighborhood of Poble Sec, at the foot of Montjüic, where you can visit the Olympic site.', 'Start your day with breakfast in Paral.lel, before heading out for a stroll up Montjüic, where you can spend the day relaxing in a natural setting, and also visit museums such as Fundació Joan Mirò and the national gallery, MNAC.', 'Each of the bedrooms in Paral.lel comes with air conditioning, so you can enjoy tranquility and rest in the warm summer months. Browse the internet using the free Wi-Fi connection available in this hotel.', 'Paral.lel is located just a short stroll from the port and beach area of the city, and you can get to top sights such as Las Ramblas and the Gothic Quarter with its stunning cathedral.']

name: Claris Hotel & Spa GL, a Small Luxury Hotel of the World
address: Pau Claris, 150, Eixample, 08009 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located just off Barcelona’s prestigious Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard, this luxury hotel offers city views from its rooftop pool. It also has a unique art collection.', 'Built in a converted 19th century palace, Claris Hotel & Spa GL combines the classicism of the original place with modern materials and it has over 400 original pieces of art on display, giving it the Specialit Monument status. It offers free entry to the Barcelona Egyptian Museum, located next door.', 'The smart, soundproofed bedrooms feature stylish décor and hand-made furniture. Each one comes with LCD satellite TV, sofa and pieces of Roman, Egyptian and Hindu artwork.', 'The hotel’s Terraza del Claris Restaurant serves gourmet Mediterranean food on the roof terrace overlooking the characteristic rooftops of the Eixample quarter. The Mr Kao Restaurant offers classic recipes from Chinese gastronomy combined with Mediterranean ingredients and local produce.', 'The Claris is just 5 minutes’ walk from Gaudí’s Casa Batlló and La Pedrera. The Ramblas is around 10 minutes’ walk away.']

address: Gran Via de les Corts Catalanes, 454, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Eric Vökel Gran Via Suites are boutique apartments set in central Barcelona, 10 minutes’ walk from Plaza de Espanya Square. These chic apartments offer free WiFi access.', 'Each air-conditioned apartment at Eric Vökel has attractive, contemporary décor. All accommodations has a well-equipped kitchenette and a spacious living area with a flat-screen TV.', 'There are several bars and cafés within 100 m of the Suites. Set on Gran Via Avenue, the apartments have easy access to a range of supermarkets and shops.', 'The Vökel is just 20 minutes’ walk from Montjuïc Mountain and Catalunya’s National Art Museum. The famous Las Ramblas and the surrounding Gothic Quarter can be reached in 10 minutes, by Metro.']

name: Mothern by Pillow
address: Ronda Sant Pere, 15, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Mothern by Pillow! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located just outside Barcelona’s central Plaza Catalunya Square, Mothern by Pillow offers bright, air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi and satellite TV. Buses to Barcelona Airport stop 100 m away.', 'Mothern by Pillow is located next to Passeig de Gracia Boulevard, 601 m from Gaudi’s famous Casa Batlló and a 5-minute walk from the Ramblas and the Gothic Quarter. Metro and regional train services stop at Catalunya Station, just 50 m away.', 'Set in a restored 19th- century building, the Mothern by Pillow features simple, modern décor throughout. It has a 24-hour reception with a tour desk and ticket service.', 'A varied buffet breakfast is available in the dining room. You can also find a wide range of cafés, tapas bars and restaurants in the surrounding streets.']

name: Ecozentric
address: Balmes, 23 Principal 2, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Ecozentric! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Ecozentric is in central Barcelona, just a 5-minute walk from Plaza Catalunya and Gaudí’s Casa Batlló. This eco-friendly property has modern rooms with free Wi-Fi and an LED TV.', 'The rooms at Ecozentric feature soundproofing and air conditioning. The TVs are low consumption, and the bed sheets are made of organic cotton. Each one has a private bathroom with a rain-effect shower.', 'The guesthouse has free tea, coffee and cookies throughout the day. There is a lounge where you can relax.', 'MACBA Modern Art Museum and the Raval district are a 7-minute walk from Ecozentric, and you can walk to the Boqueria Market and Palau de la Música Auditorium in 13 minutes. Airport buses leave from Plaza Catalunya.', 'Ecozentric donates part of every booking to the reforestation of woodlands.']

Breakfast can also be requested in your room, and a light early breakfast is available.', 'Staff in the Guest Relations department can help you throughout your stay and advise you on what to see and do in Barcelona.', 'The hotel is just one block away from Gaudí’s famous Casa Batlló. To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'The Petit Palace Boqueria Garden is set in a historic 19th-century building by La Boqueria Market, 11 m from Las Ramblas, and offers free high-speed WiFi and free bicycle use (subject to availability).', 'Each room at the Petit Palace Boqueria Garden includes a flat-screen TV and laptop safe, and a private bathroom. The hotel also offers an electric scooter hire service, subject to availability.', "The hotel's bar is set by a private courtyard and garden with hundred-year-old trees, a listed site of architectural heritage in Barcelona.", "Petit Palace Boqueria Garden is located in Barcelona's Gothic Quarter, just a 1-minute walk from Liceu Metro Station, offering convenient transport around the city. Plaça Catalunya Square is 801 m away, and you can walk to Barcelona Port in 8 minutes."]

name: Weflating City Center
address: Roger de Lluria, 40 3rd to 7th floor, Eixample, 08009 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Weflating City Center! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'These stylish apartments and rooms are located in the chic Eixample district of central Barcelona, just 350 m from the famous Passeig de Gracia Boulevard and Metro Station. They offer a plasma TV and free Wi-Fi.', 'The air-conditioned Weflating City Center are spacious, bright and offer two or three bedrooms. The modern kitchen includes a washing machine, oven and a dishwasher.', 'There are several bars, restaurants and shops within 5 minutes- walk of the apartments, and many of the city’s most popular monuments can be reached easily by foot.', 'Gaudi’s La Pedrera and La Rambla are both just 10 minutes’ walk away. The Barceloneta area with its beach can be reached by metro in around 10 minutes.', 'Direct busses to El Prat Airport run from outside El Corte Ingles department store on Plaza Catalunya Square, 601 m away. Various busses, trains and metros also run from here.']

name: Catalonia Square 4* Sup
address: Ronda Sant Pere, 9, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Square 4* Sup! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Featuring an outdoor pool and a fitness center, Catalonia Square is located in Barcelona’s historic center. The 4-star hotel is only 100 m from Plaça Catalunya and offers free Wi-Fi', 'Each air-conditioned room has wooden floors and modern décor and comes with a satellite flat-screen TV, mini-bar and a battery charger for iPhone/iPad. Featuring a hairdryer, private bathrooms also include free toiletries and towels. Private pool and terrace are available in some rooms.', 'Guests can enjoy drinks, snacks and traditional tapas at Catalonia Square Bar. The breakfast is served until 12:00. Room service is also available.', 'La Rambla and the Gothic District are only 5 minutes’ walk from the hotel. Within 984 feet, guests can find the metro stations of Passeig de Gracia, Plaça Catalunya and Urquinaona, offering connection to most parts of Barcelona.']

name: Sunotel Central
address: Gran Vía De Les Corts Catalanes, 570, Eixample, 08011 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Sunotel Central! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", "Featuring a rooftop swimming pool and hot tub with views of Barcelona, Sunotel Central is set in the center of Barcelona, just 10 minutes' walk from Plaza Catalunya.", 'Modern rooms at Sunotel Central include free high-speed WiFi, satellite TV and a private bathroom with a hairdryer and amenities.', 'Universitat Metro Station is just 200 m from the hotel. The Ramblas, famous for its street performers, can be reached in 10 minutes by foot.', 'In the morning guests can enjoy a varied, fresh and healthy full buffet breakfast.', 'The hotel’s 24-hour reception offers a ticket booking service and luggage storage. There are computers in the lobby which guests can use for free. Meeting rooms are also available.']

name: Sunotel Club Central
address: Valencia, 157, Eixample, 08011 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Sunotel Club Central! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Featuring an outdoor swimming pool and hot tub on its terrace, Sunotel Club Central is set in Barcelona’s elegant Eixample neighborhood.', 'Each modern air-conditioned room has free, high-speed WiFi, a TV and a mini-bar. The private bathroom includes a bath, shower and hairdryer.', 'Sunotel Club Central features a cozy bar, serving snacks and drinks. There is also room service available. The hotel has a 24-hour reception, and free bicycles are available upon request and subject to availability.', 'Passeig de Gracia, with its Gaudi monuments and designer shops, is a 10-minute walk from Sunotel Club Central. The famous Las Ramblas Boulevard and Plaza Catalunya are a 15-minute walk from the hotel. Barcelona Airport is 9.3 mi away, and you can catch an airport bus in Plaza Catalunya.']

address: Sant Pau, 9-11, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hotel España is located in a 19th-century building in central Barcelona, within 100 m of the Ramblas and Liceu Theater and 200 m from Boqueria Market. Its Mediterranean restaurant is run by famous chef Martín Berasategui. There is free high-speed WiFi available throughout.', 'The stylish and elegant rooms include a flat-screen TV and air conditioning. They also come with a modern bathroom.', 'Hotel España offers a variety of drinks and cocktails at Bar Arnau in winter and AlAire rooftop terrace bar in summer. There is also a small swimming pool.', 'Liceu Metro Station is 100 m away and the Gothic Quarter is less than 5 minutes’ walk away.']

name: HCC St. Moritz
address: Diputació, 262-264, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Set in a listed 19th-century building and 5 minutes’ walk from Gaudí’s Casa Batlló, the St. Moritz offers stylish accommodations. It features modern, air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi and LCD satellite TV.', 'The Hotel HCC St. Moritz maintains its original central staircase and marble reception. Its rooms offer simple, classic décor with a mini-bar and a private bathroom with a hairdryer, slippers and toiletries.', 'A varied buffet breakfast is served daily, and you can enjoy a range of Mediterranean dishes for dinner in the St Gallen Restaurant, where menus use fresh, seasonal produce.', 'Passeig de Gràcia and its Metro Station are just 5 minutes’ walk from the hotel, and Plaza de Catalunya and Las Ramblas are one stop away. Barcelona Port is just over 0.6 mi from the St. Moritz.']

name: Ikonik Ramblas
address: La Rambla, 22-24, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Ikonik Ramblas! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'This ultra-modern hotel is right on central Barcelona’s Ramblas, just 293 m from the seafront promenade. It has stylish, air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi and flat-screen satellite TV.', 'The rooms at the Ikonik Ramblas feature parquet floors and chic décor. Each one has a minibar and a private bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'The staff at the 24-hour front desk can provide information about what Barcelona has to offer. They can also help booking tickets for guided tours, live shows and other events.', 'Many famous sites are within easy walking distance of the property. The Liceu Theatre is a quarter mile away, and Plaza Real is a 3-minute walk away. Barcelona Cathedral is less than half a kilometer away.', 'You can walk to Barcelona’s famous Boquería Market in 7 minutes from the hotel. Airport buses leave from Plaza Catalunya, a 15-minute walk away.']

name: Hotel SB Icaria Barcelona
address: Avinguda Icaria, 195, Sant Martí, 08005 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located 300 m from Barcelona’s Nova Icaria Beach, Hotel SB Icaria Barcelona offers a gym, sauna and outdoor pool with sun terrace and hot tub. Rooms include free Wi-Fi and flat-screen satellite TV.', 'The Hotel SB Icaria Barcelona’s stylish modern rooms feature wooden floors and adjustable lighting. Each room has a mini-bar, safe and private bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'The hotel’s elegant restaurant serves Mediterranean market cuisine. There is also a bar and a garden terrace.', 'Hotel SB Icaria Barcelona is located in the Olympic Port area, a 10-minute walk from Ciutadella Park and Barcelona Zoo. Ciutadella Metro Station is 801 m away, and is just 2 stops from Barcelona Cathedral and the historic Gothic Quarter.']

name: Ibis Barcelona Centro (Sagrada Familia)
address: Carrer Napòls, 230-232, Eixample, 08013 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in Barcelona, 1.7 mi from Somorrostro Beach, Ibis Barcelona Centro (Sagrada Familia) provides accommodations with a bar, private parking and a shared lounge. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and a concierge service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The hotel features family rooms.', 'All units are equipped with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a kettle, a shower, a hairdryer and a wardrobe. At the hotel every room is fitted with a private bathroom.', 'A buffet breakfast is available daily at Ibis Centro.', 'Reservations made with breakfast included are not going to include the breakfast for the kids of 11 years old or under, this service will have an extra cost of 4€ per kid and per night.', 'Popular points of interest near the accommodations include Sagrada Familia, La Pedrera and Casa Batllo. The nearest airport is Barcelona El Prat Airport, 8.7 mi from Ibis Barcelona Centro (Sagrada Familia).']

name: BCN Apartments 41
address: Casp, 41, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at BCN Apartments 41! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'The elegant, air-conditioned apartments at BCN Apartments 41 include free Wi-Fi and flat-screen satellite TV. They are located just over a quarter mile from Barcelona’s Plaza Catalunya and Passeig de Gracia.', 'The bright, spacious apartments each include a lounge area with sofas. Their kitchenettes have an oven, microwave and dishwasher.', 'Many bars, restaurants and shops can be found in the surrounding streets of the Eixample District. The fashionable Born area is just a 10-minute walk away.', 'The staff can provide tourist information, and the Arc de Triomf, Ciutadella Park and Barcelona Cathedral can all be reached in a 10-minute walk. Port Vell is 20 minutes away by foot.', 'Urquinaona Metro Station is just under a quarter of a kilometer from the apartments and provides service to the beach. Airport buses are available at Plaza Catalunya. Private parking in the same building is available for an extra fee.']

name: Grupotel Gravina
address: Gravina, 12, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Grupotel Gravina! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", "Housed in an attractive 19th-century building, Grupotel Gravina is located just off Plaza Catalunya, Barcelona’s main square, 5 minutes' walk from Las Ramblas. It offers 24-hour reception and modern rooms with free WiFi and satellite TV.", 'The Hotel Gravina is just 5 minutes’ walk from the MACBA Modern Art Gallery and 15 minutes from Gaudí’s La Pedrera and Casa Batlló. Catalunya Metro Station, located 100 m from the hotel, connects you with the rest of the city.', 'The air-conditioned rooms at Grupotel Gravina feature modern furniture and some have parquet floors. They are equipped with a work desk and a private bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'The hotel has a smart bar where you can get a snack or a drink. hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Barcelona 505! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Catalonia Barcelona 505 offers spacious rooms with free Wi-Fi and an outdoor swimming pool in Barcelona’s Sant Gervasi area. From El Putxet Train Station, 400 m away, you can reach the center in 15 minutes.', 'The hotel is close to important medical centers, such as the Teknon Clinic, Sant Jordi Clinic, Dexeus and Barraquer. It is also next to the Blue Tram, which takes you to the cable car for Tibidabo.', 'Air-conditioned rooms have a satellite TV, a safe and mini-bar. There is a work desk, and the private bathroom comes with a hairdryer and amenities.', 'The restaurant C50&5 offers international cuisine. There is a bar and room service is available.', 'You can hire a car from the 24-hour front desk. On-site parking is offered for an additional charge, and the hotel has easy access to the B20 Motorway.']

name: Hotel Derby
address: Loreto, 21-25, Les Corts, 08029 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Situated 305 m from L’Illa Diagonal Shopping Center, the Derby is a 20-minute walk from FC Barcelona’s Camp Nou stadium. Each air conditioned room offers flat-screen satellite TV and free internet access.', 'The stylish Derby Hotel has an impressive collection of Catalan art, including pieces by Miró and Tàpies. Rooms have functional design and parquet floors. They all include a safe and a minibar.', "Drinks and light meals are served in the Derby’s coffee shop, The Times. L'Illa Shopping Center offers a range of restaurants.", 'Located just 10 m away, the Gran Derby Hotel allows guests access to its gym, sauna and swimming pool. Hospital Clinic Metro Station is half a kilometer away, while the Feria Trade Fair in Plaza Espanya can be reached in a 20-minute walk.']

name: Capri by Fraser Barcelona
address: Sancho de Ávila, 32-34, Sant Martí, 08018 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This motorcycle-friendly hotel is 3 Metro stops from Plaza Catalunya and 15 minutes’ walk from the Barcelona’s beaches. There is free WiFi available throughout.', 'Capri by Fraser Barcelona offers chic air-conditioned and spacious suites and apartments with a flat-screen cable TV and a seating area. There is a fully-equipped kitchenette, a work desk and a safe, and the private bathroom comes with a hairdryer and amenities.', 'The property has a free self-service laundry room open 24 hours a day and a gym.', 'For guests coming by motorcycle, Capri by Fraser offers free indoor parking with direct elevator to the rooms and a “pit stop” service including complete toolkit for small repairs and chain lubricant, free suede, helmet visor cleaner, battery charger and compressor to check the pressure level of tires.', 'Capri by Fraser Barcelona offers a buffet breakfast every day and a set menu at lunch time during week days. Room service is also available.', 'The hotel has a 24-hour front desk.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel America Barcelona! name: Mercure Barcelona Condor
address: Vía Augusta, 127, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08006 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This casual-style, urban hotel is set in Barcelona’s quiet Sarrià-Sant Gervasi district, 10 minutes’ from the center via nearby Sant Gervasi FGC Train Station. It offers modern and contemporary rooms with views.', 'The bright, air-conditioned rooms at Mercure Barcelona Condor come with free WiFi, satellite TV, a work desk, mini-bar, safe and private bathroom with hairdryer. Some rooms also have a terrace.', "A buffet breakfast is served daily at the hotel's restaurant. Room service and laundry facilities are also available.", 'Guests have free access to the fitness center which overlooks the Tibidabo mountain and the city. Massage services are available for a supplement. Events and meetings can also be catered for.', 'There are various bars, shops and pleasant squares within 5 minutes’ walk in the Gracia district. The famous Passeig de Gracia Boulevard, with Gaudi’s La Pedrera, as well as Park Güell are just 15 minutes away by foot.', 'Diagonal Avenue , a popular shopping area, is just 751 m away from Mercure Barcelona Condor and Muntaner FGC Station is a 3-minute walk away.']

name: The Corner Hotel
address: Mallorca 178, Eixample, 08036 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at The Corner Hotel! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located in Barcelona, 0.7 mi from Casa Batllo, The Corner Hotel provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, private parking, a bar and a terrace. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. Guests can have a drink at the snack bar.', 'All units at the hotel include air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels,and a private bathroom with a bath or shower, bathrobes and slippers. At The Corner Hotel every room comes with bed linen and towels.', 'A buffet breakfast is available daily at the accommodations.', 'Popular points of interest near The Corner Hotel include Passeig de Gracia, Plaça Catalunya and La Pedrera. The nearest airport is Barcelona El Prat Airport, 7.5 mi from the hotel.']

name: Sant Jordi Hostels Sagrada Familia
address: Freser, 5, Sant Martí, 08026 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Sant Jordi Hostels Sagrada Familia! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Sant Jordi Hostels Sagrada Familia is located just moments from Gaudi’s Sagrada Familia Church. It offers dorm rooms, private rooms and apartment-style accommodations. Free WiFi access in available most areas.', 'Featuring skateboard-themed décor and an indoor mini-ramp, the hostel offers a shared guest kitchen and lounge, as well as a stylish lobby with computer facilities.', 'All dormitory rooms and triple rooms are located in the hostel area, and have heating, air-conditioning and individual lockers and shelves with a reading light and plug.', 'All private double and single rooms are located upstairs from the hostel in the apartment-style area, and include heating and fans. Guests in this area have use of a shared kitchen and living room.', 'Sant Jordi Hostel is less than 5 minutes’ walk from Sant Pau Metro Station, giving easy access to all parts of the city.']

Each room is air-conditioned and includes a safe.']

name: Hotel California
address: Rauric, 14, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain

The hotel offers rooms with a balcony, air conditioning and free Wi-Fi.', 'Each soundproofed room includes a flat-screen TV and wardrobe.The private bathroom comes with a hairdryer and free toiletries. Towels and bed linen are provided.', 'A breakfast buffet is available at Hotel Califorina, which also offers a bar and room service. Guests can enjoy a shared lounge.', 'La Boqueria Market is located 300 m from the property, while Plaça Catalunya is 10 minutes’ walk away. La Barceloneta Beach can be reached in 20 minutes on foot. Liceu Metro Station is 200 m from the hotel']

name: Pestana Arena Barcelona

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Pestana Arena Barcelona! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Pestana Arena Barcelona is less than 5 minutes’ walk from Barcelona’s Plaza Espanya and Fira Exhibition Center. It offers a gym, sauna and modern, air-conditioned rooms with free wired internet access.', 'Some rooms offers free use of the Maritimo Meeting Room, up to 12 people, for private meetings.', 'Pestana Arena Barcelona is just 3 minutes’ walk from Las Arenas Shopping Center and you can walk to Sants Station in 8 minutes. You can get to the Rambla in 5 minutes from Plaza Espanya Metro.', 'Rooms feature parquet floors and stylish décor. Each one has work desk, a pillow menu and an LCD TV with satellite channels.', "The hotel’s restaurant serves Mediterranean food and has a terrace. There is also a bar where you can get a snack or a drink. The hotel's breakfast includes products for celiacs."]

name: Exe Ramblas Boquería
address: Rambla de Sant Josep, 91-93, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Exe Ramblas Boquería is located right on Barcelona’s famous Las Ramblas, next to La Boquería Market. The stylish, air-conditioned rooms offer free WiFi, flat-screen satellite TV and a private balcony.', 'Exe Ramblas Boquería features elegant modern décor, with hardwood floors and designer furniture. The soundproofed rooms have views of Las Ramblas or the colorful Boqueria Market.', 'A varied buffet breakfast is served in the Exe Ramblas Boquería’s bright dining room. The Boquería is an ideal place to sample characteristic tapas and fresh fruit, while numerous restaurants and bars can be found nearby.', 'Barcelona Cathedral and Plaça Catalunya are both within 400 m of the hotel. Liceu Metro Station is just 100 m away.']

name: Duquesa Suites Barcelona
address: Plaça Antonio López 5, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Set the center of Barcelona, 400 m from Picasso Museum and Barceloneta Metro Station, Duquesa Suites Barcelona features a year-round outdoor plunge pool, sun terrace and free WiFi. It is housed in a building from the 18th century with the Specialty Monument status.', 'Rooms at this hotel come with 1 extra large double bed, a sofa bed and a bathroom with free toiletries and a hairdryer. Rooms have air conditioning, a flat-screen TV and capsule coffee machine.', 'Please note that the hotel reserves the right to pre-authorize credit cards prior to arrival. When booking more than 3 rooms, different policies and additional charges may apply. Buffet breakfast is served at Hotel Duquesa de Cardona. Local City Tax pending to be paid at Front Desk.', 'Plaza Reial is 500 m from Duquesa Suites Barcelona, while La Seu, Cathedral of Barcelona is 601 m from the property. The nearest airport is Barcelona El Prat Airport, 8.1 mi from Duquesa Suites Barcelona.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Gaudi Flats! name: Duquesa Suites Barcelona
address: Plaça Antonio López 5, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Set the center of Barcelona, 400 m from Picasso Museum and Barceloneta Metro Station, Duquesa Suites Barcelona features a year-round outdoor plunge pool, sun terrace and free WiFi. It is housed in a building from the 18th century with the Specialty Monument status.', 'Rooms at this hotel come with 1 extra large double bed, a sofa bed and a bathroom with free toiletries and a hairdryer. Rooms have air conditioning, a flat-screen TV and capsule coffee machine.', 'Please note that the hotel reserves the right to pre-authorize credit cards prior to arrival. When booking more than 3 rooms, different policies and additional charges may apply. Buffet breakfast is served at Hotel Duquesa de Cardona. Local City Tax pending to be paid at Front Desk.', 'Plaza Reial is 500 m from Duquesa Suites Barcelona, while La Seu, Cathedral of Barcelona is 601 m from the property. The nearest airport is Barcelona El Prat Airport, 8.1 mi from Duquesa Suites Barcelona.']

name: Royal Ramblas
address: Las Ramblas, 117, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Royal Ramblas! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", "Royal Ramblas is located on Barcelona's famous Ramblas, 100 m from Plaza de Catalunya. It offers elegant and modern rooms with air conditioning, plasma TV, free Wi-Fi, and private parking. Some rooms provide magnificent views of the Ramblas.", 'The Hotel has a meeting room with magnificent views of the Ramblas.', 'It offers a buffet breakfast with various regional products and homemade pastries in the La Poma restaurant with impressive views of Las Ramblas where you can also taste Mediterranean food.', 'The Royal Ramblas Hotel is ideally located with access to all public transport and a 5-minute walk from the elegant Passeig de Gràcia, where you will find numerous restaurants and exclusive shops. The old town is within walking distance, as well as the Mercat de la Boqueria and the MACBA. The beach is 20 minutes away.', "The Royal Ramblas Barcelona's tour desk offers useful information about the city and car rental services. It also manages the airport transfer service."]

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Vincci Maritimo! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Vincci Marítimo is a 10-minute walk from Barcelona’s Diagonal Mar Shopping Center and the CCIB Convention Centre. It has bright, stylish rooms with flat-screen satellite TV and free Wi-Fi throughout.', 'The air-conditioned rooms at the Hotel Marítimo feature modern décor, with parquet floors and relaxing images of the sea. They include a pillow menu and the private bathrooms contain a hairdryer. Rooms offer views of the charming Japanese Zen garden or Diagonal Mar Park.', "The hotel’s Jardí de Mar Restaurant serves Mediterranean food using fresh ingredients. The hotel's breakfast includes products for celiacs. The Ikebana Lounge Bar has snacks, tapas and cocktails which can be enjoyed on the terrace.", 'The hotel’s front desk is open 24 hours a day, allowing you greater flexibility during your stay. Laundry and car rental services are also available from the front desk.', 'The Vincci Marítimo is just over a quarter mile from Mar Bella Beach. Selva de Mar Metro Station is a 2-minute walk from the hotel, connecting you to the center of the city in 15 minutes.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Pars Tailor's Hostel! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", "Set around 10 minutes’ walk from Plaza Catalunya and Las Ramblas, Pars Tailor's Hostal offers air-conditioned dorm rooms, free Wi-Fi, a fully equipped kitchen and a terrace.", 'Designed as a 1930s tailor shop, it features vintage décor and wooden furnishings. Bathrooms are shared and bed linen is included.', "Tailor's Hostel features a guest lounge area and a games room with a pool table. Urgell Metro Station and Sant Antoni Metro Station are both less than 5 minutes’ walk away.']

name: Acta CITY47
address: Nicaragua, 47, Sants-Montjuïc, 08029 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Acta CITY47 is 5 minutes’ walk from Barcelona Sants Train Station and 15 minutes from the Fira Exhibition Center. It offers a 24-hour reception and air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi.', 'The rooms at Acta CITY47 feature simple, modern décor and a private bathroom. Each one comes with a TV, free safe, and a work desk. Guests have free access to an ironing room open 24 hours.', 'The hotel’s modern Nass City restaurant serves international food and a gluten-free breakfast is available on prior request. There is also a bar where you can get a snack or a drink.', 'The Acta CITY47 is 20 minutes’ walk from Barcelona FC’s Camp Nou Stadium. Sants Metro Station connects you with the center of Barcelona in 15 minutes.']

name: Sansi Pedralbes
address: Avenida Pearson, 1-3, Les Corts, 08034 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Peaceful gardens and stylish rooms with free Wi-Fi and TV are offered at Sansi Pedralbes.', 'It is just 250 m from Pedralbes Monastery and 701 m from UPC University.\nIESE University is just 5 minutes walking and ESADE University 200 m from the hotel.', 'Decorated in soft blues and browns, this design hotel’s air-conditioned rooms come with a mini-bar, safe and iron. Bathrooms include toiletries.', 'Buses to central Barcelona stop within 21 m of the hotel, and city tour buses stop at Pedralbes Monastery.\nReina Elisenda Station is 801 m away and Barcelona Airport is a 15-minute drive away.', 'There are various popular bars and cafés in Sarrià, a 10-minute walk from the hotel.', 'You can also enjoy a varied breakfast and Catalan cuisine in the Sansi’s elegant restaurant.', 'A heated indoor pool, saunas and aromatherapy showers are offered in the hotel’s spa, available at an extra cost. Massages can be arranged on request.']

name: Alba Hotel
address: Hospital, 83, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Alba Hotel! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'This hotel is set in the heart of the cosmopolitan city of Barcelona, just a short distance from Las Ramblas and within walking distance of attractions such as the Liceu opera house and Plaça Catalunya.', 'The Hotel Alba is located in Barcelona’s old town, and its beautiful façade is listed for its artistic interest. Inside, relax in a spacious bedroom with a balcony, private bathroom, and air conditioning.', 'Stroll down the colorful Ramblas to the seafront, or enjoy Cava and tapas in the famous Boqueria food market. Just a short walk away, the narrow streets of the Gothic Quarter are full of shops, bars and restaurants.', 'The Alba boasts convenient public transportation access, with Liceu metro station only 275 m away. From there you can travel quickly and conveniently to attractions including the Fira de Barcelona and Gaudi’s incredible Parc Güell.']

name: W Barcelona
address: Plaça Rosa dels Vents, 1 - Passeig Joan de Borbo, Ciutat Vella, 08039 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['W Barcelona is a striking sail-like structure next to Barceloneta Beach, offering breathtaking design and fantastic views over Barcelona. It features a spa, infinity pool, rooftop bar and luxurious rooms.', 'The W Hotel’s impressive rooms feature avant-garde design and views of the Mediterranean or the city. They all come with a chaise lounge, flat-screen TV, iPod docking station and rainfall shower.', 'The W has a stylish gourmet restaurant, FIRE; and you can enjoy a cocktail with panoramic views over the city and sea at ECLIPSE rooftop bar, located on the 26th floor. Cocktails are also offered in the W Lounge. The SALT Beach Club & Restaurant has a menu of innovative burgers accompanied by specially designed cocktails to live the ultimate burger by the beach experience.', 'There are two pools, SUN Deck and WET Deck, which are surrounded by decking with loungers. The hotel also has direct beach access. Facilities at the W Spa include a hot tub, sauna and steam room, and a brand new relaxation area, GETAWAY, is available from 2018. A wide range of relaxation and beauty treatments is available.', 'The W is 20 minutes’ walk from Barceloneta Metro Station, and buses stop outside the hotel.']

name: Casa Barcelo Hostel Barcelona
address: Corsega 226, ENTRESUELO, Eixample, 08036 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Casa Barcelo Hostel Barcelona! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set in Barcelona’s stylish Eixample district, Barcelo Hostel offers air-conditioned dormitory rooms with free Wi-Fi. Located 601 m from Passeig de Gracia, the hostel features a terrace, 24-hour reception and shared kitchens.', 'Each bright dormitory has bunk beds and lockers. There is access to shared bathrooms with showers and hairdryers. Bicycles are not allowed', 'Barcelo Hostel offers 2 shared kitchens, including a microwave, fridge and kitchenware. There are also 2 air-conditioned lounge areas with sofas and a TV. You can find a variety of shops, restaurants and bars within a 5-minute walk of the hostel.', 'Diagonal Metro Station is 500 m from Barcelo Hostel and Plaza Catalunya is 2 stops away, on Line 3. Staff at the hostel can give you tourist information about the area.']

name: Hostal Barcelona
address: Roser, 40, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["Located 15 minutes' walk from Las Ramblas and Plaça Espanya, Hostal Barcelona has rooms with air conditioning, TV and free Wi-Fi. Famous for its theaters, Parallel Avenue is 100 m away.", 'Hostal Barcelona can provide tourist information, assist with ticket reservations including the Barcelona Tourist Bus, and help arrange car/bike rental. There is an internet terminal in reception. A luggage storage service is available and all rooms have a safe.', 'A breakfast buffet is served from 07:30 to 10:30, while cold and hot drinks and pastries are available 24 hours a day. Guests also have access to a microwave. There are many supermarkets, restaurants and bars in the surroundings.', 'Parallel Metro Station and many bus routes are 100 m from Hostal Barcelona. The Fira Convention Center is 12 minutes away by public transport. Montjuïc is a 5-minute walk from the guest house, and the Old Harbor can be reached in 20 minutes on foot.']

name: Hotel Àmbit Barcelona
address: Roger de Llúria, 17, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel Àmbit Barcelona! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located 400 m from Barcelona’s Plaça Catalunya, Hotel Àmbit Barcelona offers modern, air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi. Some rooms have a terrace or balcony.', 'You will find a 24-hour front desk at the property, where staff can help with bike hire, car hire and tourist information. Free coffee is available 24 hours on the first floor.', "The shopping street, Portal de l'Angel, is 500 m from Hotel Àmbit Barcelona, while Barcelona Cathedral is 801 m away. There are many restaurants in the area."]

name: Hotel SB Glow **** Sup
address: 154 Carrer de Badajoz, Sant Martí, 08018 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hotel SB Glow **** Sup has a restaurant, fitness center, a bar and shared lounge in Barcelona. This 4-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and a concierge service. Free WiFi is available and private parking can be arranged at an extra charge.', 'At the hotel, each room comes with a closet. Rooms contain air conditioning, a safety deposit box and a flat-screen TV, and certain accommodations at Hotel SB Glow **** Sup have a balcony. name: Pensión San Ramón
address: San Ramón, 15, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Pensión San Ramón is located in Barcelona’s Raval district, just 350 m from the Rambla. It offers a 24-hour reception and air-conditioned rooms with a flat-screen TV.', 'The guest house has vending machines for drinks, and there is a common area with a microwave for guests’ use. There are many restaurants and bars in the surrounding streets.', 'Staff at reception can provide information about what Barcelona has to offer. Pensión San Ramón is 5 minutes’ walk from the Sala Apolo Nightclub and Paral·lel Metro Station, which connects you with the rest of the city.']

name: Hotel Vilamarí
address: Vilamari, 34-36, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hotel Vilamarí is set 250 m from Plaza de Espanya Metro Station and the Fira de Barcelona Exhibition Center. This design hotel features a terrace and a small gym with Turkish Bath.', 'The Vilamarí’s rooms have simple, elegant décor and dark wood furniture. Each room includes flat-screen satellite TV. The stylish bathrooms come with amenities and a hairdryer. The hotel features centrally controlled air conditioned or heating depending on the season.', 'Barcelona’s MNAC Art Museum and the Magic Fountains are within a 10-minute walk of the hotel. Las Arenas Shopping Center is just 200 m away. Barcelona Port is a 15-minute metro ride away and Barcelona Beach can be reached in 35 minutes.', 'The hotel’s restaurant offers modern versions of traditional Catalan cuisine. Guests can enjoy meals or drinks outside on the terrace. The hotel also has a café-bar and 24-hour room service.']

It offers a 24-hour gym, and the rooftop pool offers impressive views of Barcelona.', 'The bright soundproofed rooms at the Hotel Barcelona Condal Mar are spacious and feature air conditioning, satellite TV and free Wi-Fi. At the accommodation rooms are equipped with bed linen and towels.', 'Hotel Casa Sagnier offers a continental or buffet breakfast.', 'The hotel offers 5-star accommodations with a sauna and terrace.', 'Popular points of interest near Hotel Casa Sagnier include Casa Batllo, Passeig de Gracia and Passeig de Gracia Metro Station. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat, 16.1 km from the accommodation, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.']

name: Aspasios Rambla Catalunya Suites
address: Rambla de Catalunya 42, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['These chic apartments are set on Barcelona’s stylish Rambla de Catalunya, 150 m from Passeig de Gracia Boulevard. There is free WiFi available throughout.', 'Apartments at Aspasios Rambla Catalunya Suites feature contemporary decor, a sofa bed, and plasma TV while kitchens have a dishwasher, washing machine, tumble drier and Nespresso coffee maker.', 'There are several bars, restaurants and shops within 5 minutes’ walk and Plaza Catalunya is 400 m away.', 'Las Ramblas and the Gothic Quarter are 10 minutes’ walk away and Gaudí’s La Pedrera and Casa Batllo are within 5 minutes’ walk.', 'The Aspasios Rambla Catalunya apartments are 3 minutes’ walk from Passeig de Gracia Metro and Train Station, with direct trains to Barcelona El Prat Airport.', 'The pictures at the top of this page are a selection of the different apartments located in the Eixample area. Please select a date and click on the apartments to see the pictures of the individual apartments.']

name: Hotel El Palace Barcelona
address: Gran Via de les Corts Catalanes, 668, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel El Palace Barcelona! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Hotel El Palace Barcelona is located in Eixample District, close to the Ramblas, the main shopping area and Barcelona’s main tourist attractions. It offers a Mayan-style luxury spa. A limousine service with a chauffeur is available on request.', 'Opened in 1919, this hotel features a neo-classical façade and stylish air-conditioned rooms with classic decor. Each room is spacious and comes with satellite TV, desk, mini-bar and a private bathroom with hairdryer, bathrobe and slippers.', "There are 2 restaurants: L'Éclair, located at the hall, and the Winter Garden Restaurant, set at the Roof Terrace; guests can also enjoy a cocktail at the Bluesman Cocktail Bar.", 'Hotel El Palace Barcelona has a Mayan-style spa with a Temazcal Sauna. Other facilities at this hotel include both fitness and business center and an outdoor pool.', 'Staff at Hotel El Palace Barcelona can provide information about the area. Passeig de Gràcia Metro and Railway Station as well as Urquinaona Metro station are less than 5 minutes’ walk of the hotel.', 'Gaudí’s Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are approximately 15 minutes’ walk away.']

address: Calabria 90-92, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Offering a rooftop pool with a large sun terrace, TWO Hotel Barcelona by Axel is located in the heart of the gay district of Barcelona, 1.2 mi from Barceloneta Beach.', 'The hetero-friendly hotel offers on-site private parking. There is also a 24-hour reception and guests can get information on the gay scene and the city at the on-site tour desk. On the rooftop guests will also find the Sky bar, gym, steam bath and a massage room.', 'Each room here will provide you with air conditioning and a mini-bar. Featuring a shower, private bathroom also comes with a hairdryer. A safety deposit box and a universal phone charger are also provided.', 'Guests can sample a drink at the rooftop bar, while taking in stunning city views or enjoy the delicious cocktails served in the Lounge Bar. A buffet breakfast is available and free high-speed WiFi access is provided throughout.', 'Staff can give information about the surrounding area, which is known as "Gayxample" because of its lively gay nightlife.', "The hotel is 2 minutes' walk from Rocafort Metro Station and Plaça d'Espanya, with direct busses to Barcelona Airport, is a 10-minute walk away. Paral·lel, with bars, restaurants, clubs and theaters is 0.8 mi from TWO Hotel Barcelona by Axel."]

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Ofelias Hotel 4* Sup! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set just off Gran Vía and a 2-minute walk from Plaza Espanya Metro Station and the Fira Exhibition Center, Ofelias Hotel offers stylish rooms with free Wi-Fi. hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Cosmo Apartments Consell de Cent - Plaza Universitat! It is 300 m from Urgell Metro Station, just 2 stops from Las Ramblas and Plaza de Catalunya.', 'Each air-conditioned apartment has chic, contemporary décor with chrome finishes and trendy furnishings. name: Travelodge Barcelona Poblenou
address: Llull, 170, Sant Martí, 08005 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description:
['This modern hotel has 250 spacious and fully equipped rooms, a Snack-Bar open 24 hours where clients can enjoy a buffet breakfast, as well as light meals for lunch and dinner. It also has vending machines and private paid parking. All its facilities are perfectly adapted and accessible for people with reduced mobility.
It is a hotel with free and unlimited high-speed Wi-Fi in the common areas. Wi-Fi internet is available in the rooms at an extra cost.
Travelodge Barcelona Poblenou is a pet-friendly hotel that will be happy to offer you and your pet the best experience.
It is located in the traditional Poblenou neighborhood, within streets full of restaurants, bars and shops. One of the most charming neighborhoods in the city, and 601 m from the Bogatell beach. Barcelona city center can be reached in 10 minutes by metro and Barcelona’s Port Olímpic, with its vibrant night life, is just a 20-minute walk away.
This is considered the most innovative neighborhood in the city. It´s in the heart of the 22@ District and concentrates a multitude of technology and R+D companies. Therefore, thanks to its location and facilities, it is also a perfect accommodations for business trips.
Travelodge Barcelona Poblenou offers all you need to have the best experience in Barcelona city.']

name: Happy Apartments
address: Nou de la Rambla, 10, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Happy Apartments! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located 50 m from Las Ramblas and opposite Gaudí’s Palau Güell, Happy Apartments offers free Wi-Fi. Set in Barcelona’s Raval District, it features well-equipped apartments with stylish décor.', 'Each air-conditioned apartment at Happy Apartments has a spacious living room with a sofa, TV and DVD player. Kitchenettes come with an electric hob, fridge and kettle. Luggage storage is available free of charge, and towels and bed linen are included.', 'There is a selection of shops in the streets surrounding the apartments. You can find a range of bars, cafés and restaurants on Las Ramblas and the nearby Gothic quarter.', "Liceu Metro Station is 400 m from the property, and La Boquería Market is a 5-minute walk away. Busses to the airport depart from Plaza Cataluña Square, a 10-minute walk from the apartments. Paseo de Gracia Street, known for its exclusive boutiques and Gaudi's buildings, can be reached in around 20 minutes on foot."]

name: Acta Antibes
address: Diputació, 394, Eixample, 08013 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['The Acta Antibes is set in Barcelona’s Eixample District, 10 minutes’ walk from the Sagrada Familia. This hotel features a 24-hour reception, buffet breakfast and free Wi-Fi.', 'Each of the Acta Antibes’s rooms has simple, stylish décor and wooden flooring. All air-conditioned rooms have a TV and a desk.', 'While visiting the city’s tourist attractions, guests at the Antibes can make use of its luggage storage. A gluten-free breakfast is available upon request.', 'The hotel is ideally located for visiting sights such as Gaudí’s Casa Batlló and La Pedrera, which are around 20 minutes’ walk away.', 'Plaza de Catalunya and Las Ramblas are just over one kilometer away. The nearest Metro station, Monumental, is just 200 m from the hotel.']

name: Pierre & Vacances Barcelona Sants
address: Carrer de Sants, 387, Sants-Montjuïc, 08028 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Pierre & Vacances Barcelona Sants offers stylish air-conditioned accommodations, just a 5-minute walk from FC Barcelona’s Camp Nou Stadium. Free high-speed WiFi is available.', 'Each bright apartment and studio has a well-equipped kitchenette and flat-screen satellite TV.', 'All the Pierre & Vacances apartments and studios have functional modern décor and street views. Kitchen facilities include a fridge, microwave and dishwasher. A safe is available at an extra cost.', 'Pierre & Vacances Barcelona Sants is located in the lively Sants neighborhood, home to a wide range of shops, bars and cafés.', 'Just 200 m away, Badal Metro Station connects with Sants Train Station in under 10 minutes. Collblanc metro station with direct trains to Barcelona Airport and Europa Fira is 500 m away.']

name: Feelathome Poblenou Beach Apartments
address: Bilbao, 11, Sant Martí, 08005 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Feelathome Poblenou Beach Apartments! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'These modern apartments are in the Poblenou area of Barcelona, 500 m from the beach. Free Wi-Fi is available in rooms and in public areas. The CCIB Convention Center is within walking distance.', 'Poblenou Metro is 200 m away and a 20-minute ride takes you to the city center. There is easy access to the Gaudí buildings on Passeig de Gracia.', 'The apartments located in 2 separate buildings, 211 m apart. All of them have a private kitchen complete with a washing machine, dishwasher, and oven. There is also a living room with a flat-screen TV. Some apartments have a private terrace or balcony, and a communal terrace is available on the top floor.', 'Private parking is available at an extra cost. name: Acta Voraport
address: Carrer de Ramon Turró 169-B, Sant Martí, 08005 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in Barcelona, a 10-minute walk from Bogatell Beach, Acta Voraport has accommodations with a restaurant, private parking, an outdoor swimming pool and a bar. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and an ATM, along with free WiFi throughout the property. Guests can have a drink at the snack bar.', 'The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a desk, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower. At Acta Voraport the rooms are equipped with bed linen and towels.', 'A buffet breakfast is available every morning at the accommodation.', 'Acta Voraport has a sun terrace.', 'Popular points of interest near the hotel include Mar Bella Beach, Nova Icaria Beach and Somorrostro Beach. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 19.3 km from Acta Voraport.']

name: Hotel Sant Agustí
address: Plaça Sant Agusti, 3, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Open since 1840, Sant Agustí is set in a restored convent just 150 m from Barcelona’s famous Las Ramblas. It offers free Wi-Fi and functional air-conditioned rooms with flat-screen satellite TV.', 'Each room at Hotel Sant Agustí has simple, modern design and wooden flooring. Rooms come with a safe and a bathroom with toiletries and a hairdryer. Some rooms have a private balcony.', 'The Sant Agustí serves a daily continental buffet breakfast.', 'Downstairs there are computers which guests can use for free. Reception is also open 24 hours a day.', 'Set in a quiet square, the hotel is a 2-minute walk from Liceu Metro Station and La Boqueria Market. Plaza Catalunya is within 701 m and offers various bus and train connections, including direct airport busses.']

name: HCC Taber
address: Aragón, 256, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located just an 8-minute walk from central Barcelona’s Plaza Catalunya, Hotel HCC Taber is housed in an impressive Modernist building. It has air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi.', 'The rooms at HCC Taber feature satellite TV and a minibar. The private bathroom includes a hairdryer and free toiletries.', 'The building of the HCC Taber was originally designed by the famous Barcelona architect, Domènech i Montaner, who also designed the amazing Palau de la Música Catalana. It still retains its characteristic wrought-iron balconies and large bay windows.', 'The hotel’s buffet breakfast serves a wide range of dishes, and there are also breakfast options from the menu. There is also a snack bar and room service.', 'The Ramblas are just a 10-minute walk from the hotel, and Gaudí’s iconic Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are also within a 10-minute walk. Airport buses leave from Plaza Catalunya.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Gaudi Sagrada Familia! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Just 100 m from La Sagrada Família, the stylish Gaudi Sagrada Familia apartments feature balconies and free Wi-Fi. They are within a 2-minute walk of Sagrada Familia Metro Station.', 'Each Gaudi Sagrada Familia apartment has a living-dining room with a sofa and a flat-screen TV. The kitchen includes a microwave, kettle and coffee maker. Some apartments have an oven.', 'Gaudi Avenue is lined with bars, restaurants and sidewalk cafes. A wide range of supermarkets and fast food restaurants are also within a 5-minute walk of the property.', 'The beautiful Sant Pau Hospital, a UNESCO World Heritage Site, is just under half a kilometer from Gaudi Sagrada Familia. name: AinB Eixample-Miro Apartments
address: Entença, 140, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at AinB Eixample-Miro Apartments! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'These stylish and comfortable apartments are in Barcelona’s chic Eixample district, just over a quarter mile from Gran Vía. They feature a balcony, air conditioning and free Wi-Fi, a 10-minute walk from Plaza España.', 'Apartments in Barcelona Eixample-Miro have chic decor and plenty of natural light. Lounges have a sofa bed and plasma TV and modern kitchens include a coffee machine, microwave, stove and oven.', 'There are various bars, restaurants and shops within a 5-minute walk of the property. The Las Arenas Shopping Center is a 10-minute walk away.', 'The foot of Montjuic hill, with the Olympic Stadium, MNAC and Caixa Forum Museums, is a 10-minute walk away and the Joan Miró Park is a 4-minute walk away.', 'The Eixample-Miro apartments are a 5-minute walk from Entença and Tarragona Metro Stations, connecting you with Las Ramblas in 10 minutes. Sants AVE Train Station is less than half a kilometer away.']

name: Hotel Lloret Ramblas
address: Rambla Canaletes, 125, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hotel Lloret Ramblas is situated on Barcelona’s famous Las Ramblas, just outside Plaza Catalunya Square. It offers a 24-hour front desk and air conditioned rooms with flat-screen satellite TV and free Wi-Fi.', 'Each functional room at the Lloret Ramblas Hotel features a work desk and a private bathroom with amenities. Some rooms also have a private balcony.', 'Breakfast is served in Hotel Lloret Ramblas’s beautiful lounge-dining room, which dates from the early 20th century. The lobby area has a free PC with internet and a free safe.', 'Barcelona Cathedral and the MACBA Modern Art Museum are both around 500 m from Hotel Lloret. Catalunya Metro Station is a one-minute walk away, and direct airport buses stop within 101 m.']

name: Feelathome Plaza Apartments
address: Vilardell, 16, Sants-Montjuïc, 08014 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Feelathome Plaza Apartments! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Feelathome Plaza Apartments has apartments with free Wi-Fi and heating. The apartments are 100 m from Hostafrancs Metro Station and just under half a kilometer from Plaza Espanya and Barcelona Fira Congress Centre.', 'Featuring stylish décor, all the apartments include a sitting area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels and a DVD player. Most of the apartments have a balcony or terrace. Every apartment has access to a communal rooftop terrace with views of the area.', 'Each apartment has a dining area and a kitchen equipped with a washing machine, oven and coffee machine. The bathrooms have a shower and bed linens and towels are provided.', 'Guests will find restaurants and shops within a short walk from the property. The apartments are 3.2 km from Plaza Catalunya Square and central Barcelona. Sants Train Station is a 10-minute walk from the property.']

name: Ohla Eixample
address: Còrsega, 289, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Ohla Eixample! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Offering a year-round outdoor pool with city views, Ohla Eixample is a stylish boutique hotel located 10 minutes’ walk from two of Gaudi’s major works, La Pedrera and Casa Batlló. There is free high-speed WiFi available throughout and a Clef d’Or Concierge service.', 'Each well-designed room comes with a large bed and a private bathroom with bath or a rainfall shower. There is a 55-inch flat-screen satellite TV, a mini-bar with local delicatessen and a free safe for laptops. A turndown service is also available.', 'The on-site Michelin-starred Xerta Restaurant serves traditional recipes from the Ebro Region; and a complete breakfast is also served every morning including a huge selection of local products. The hotel also has the Lobby Bar, a meeting point for both locals and hotel guests; and the Sky Bar, a creative cocktail bar.', 'Guests can enjoy a selection of high-tech fitness equipment at the on-site gym; and beauty treatments and fashion services such as personal shopper are available on prior request.', 'Ohla Eixample is conveniently located in the Eixample District, in the modernist area locally known as Quadrat d’Or - Golden Square; within 5 minutes’ walk of the emblematic Diagonal Avenue, Rambla de Catalunya and Paseo de Gracia shopping boulevards. This urban building has an eye-catching ceramic façade, made from over 1000 carved pieces that represent Vivaldi’s Four Seasons.']

name: Eric Vökel Boutique Apartments - Gran Vía Suites
address: Gran Via de les Corts Catalanes, 454, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Eric Vökel Gran Via Suites are boutique apartments set in central Barcelona, 10 minutes’ walk from Plaza de Espanya Square. These chic apartments offer free WiFi access.', 'Each air-conditioned apartment at Eric Vökel has attractive, contemporary décor. All accommodations has a well-equipped kitchenette and a spacious living area with a flat-screen TV.', 'There are several bars and cafés within 100 m of the Suites. Set on Gran Via Avenue, the apartments have easy access to a range of supermarkets and shops.', 'The Vökel is just 20 minutes’ walk from Montjuïc Mountain and Catalunya’s National Art Museum. The famous Las Ramblas and the surrounding Gothic Quarter can be reached in 10 minutes, by Metro.']

name: Charmsuites Paralel
address: Paralelo, 65, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['With stylish, well-equipped apartments with free Wi-Fi, the Charmsuites Paralel is set next to Parallel Metro Station and Victoria Theatre. It features air-conditioned accommodations with kitchen facilities.', 'These spacious, newly built apartments have attractive, modern décor. All have a spacious living room with a sofa bed and a flat-screen TV. Kitchens and kitchenettes include an electric stove, oven, kettle and coffee maker.', 'Shops, cafes and bars can be found in the streets surrounding the apartments. There are many restaurants in the nearby Raval district and around Las Ramblas, a 10-minute walk away.', "Barcelona’s Port Vell marina is just over half a kilometer from Charmsuites Paralel, and the Funicular Train to Montjuïc Hill leaves from Parallel Station. Barcelona's Fira Exhibition Centre is around a 15-minute walk away."]

name: Mesón Castilla Atiram Hotels
address: Valldonzella, 5, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Mesón Castilla is set just 100 m from Las Ramblas and Plaça Catalunya Square in central Barcelona. The hotel provides free Wi-Fi and an attractive terrace where guests can enjoy breakfast.', 'Rooms at the Mesón Castilla include ornate beds, and some have a private balcony. They come with air conditioning and a private bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'The hotel operates a 24-hour front desk, allowing guests flexibility during their stay. The tour desk can organize excursions and car rental. There are safes available at the reception for an extra charge.', 'Barcelona’s Modern Art Museum is a 5-minute walk from the hotel. The historic Gothic Quarter, with its cathedral and many bars, can be reached in 10 minutes by foot.']

name: Andante Hotel
address: Avenida de les Drassanes, 23-25, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['With a small rooftop pool offering great views over Barcelona, Andante Hotel is centrally located 350 m from Drassanes Metro Station and La Rambla. It offers free Wi-Fi and a gym.', 'Modern air-conditioned rooms feature parquet floors, a laptop safe and flat-screen satellite TV. The bathroom comes with a full-length mirror and a high-powered hairdryer.', 'A buffet breakfast with show cooking is available. A gluten-free breakfast is available upon request. There is a luggage storage room and a laundry and ironing service are offered.']

name: HCC Montblanc

hotel_description: ['Set in the Gothic Quarter and next to Urquinaona Metro Station, HCC Montblanc offers air-conditioned rooms, free Wi-Fi, satellite TV and a mini-bar.', 'Guests can enjoy a varied buffet breakfast and à la carte Mediterranean cuisine in El Racó del Montblanc restaurant.', 'Close to the Born district, Hotel Montblanc Barcelona is a 10-minute walk from Barcelona Cathedral and 500 m from Plaza de Catalunya. Palau de la Musica Concert Hall, a UNESCO World Heritage Site, is just 250 m away.', 'City tour busses and direct busses to Barcelona Airport stop at Plaza Catalunya.']

name: BBarcelona Central Boutique Apartments
address: Carrer d'Aragó 130, Eixample, 08013 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at BBarcelona Central Boutique Apartments! A microwave, a fridge and oven are also available, as well as an electric tea pot and a coffee machine.', 'Popular points of interest near the apartment include Passeig de Gracia, Plaça Catalunya and Passeig de Gracia Metro Station. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 14 km from BBarcelona Central Boutique Apartments.']

address: 50 Carrer de Ganduxer, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08021 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["Located in Barcelona, 3.1 km from La Pedrera and 3.1 km from Sants Railway Station, Isabella's House provides accommodations with free WiFi, air conditioning, a restaurant and a bar.", 'Each unit comes with a sofa, a seating area, a flat-screen TV, a well-fitted kitchen with a dining area, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a hairdryer. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 16.1 km from the accommodation."]

name: Suites Avenue
address: Passeig de Gracia, 83, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['In a striking, contemporary building on Passeig de Gràcia and facing Gaudí’s La Pedrera, Suites Avenue offers stylish accommodation. It features an outdoor swimming pool, a gym and sauna.', 'Each of the Avenue’s apartments has simple, chic décor with parquet floors and leather sofas. All apartments have a large kitchen with an oven, fridge and dishwasher. Free Wi-Fi is available.', 'The property has a concierge service, which guests can use to arrange excursions, beauty treatments and babysitting.', 'The apartments are a 5 minute walk from a selection of upscale shopping and close to a range of cafés and restaurants.', 'Casa Batlló is a 5 minute walk from the apartments, while Plaza de Catalunya and Las Ramblas are just over half a kilometer away. Diagonal Metro Station is a 2 minute walk from the Suites.']

name: Hotel Brick Barcelona
address: 304 Gran Via de les Corts Catalanes, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in Barcelona, a 7-minute walk from Magic Fountain of Montjuic, Hotel Brick Barcelona features views of the city. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and a business center, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The hotel has family rooms.', 'The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a desk, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower. At Hotel Brick Barcelona the rooms come with bed linen and towels.', 'A buffet breakfast is available every morning at the accommodation.', 'Sants Railway Station is a 14-minute walk from Hotel Brick Barcelona, while Palau Sant Jordi is 1.8 km from the property. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 12.1 km from the hotel.']

name: Olivia Plaza Hotel
address: Plaza de Catalunya, 19, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located on Plaza Catalunya in the center of Barcelona, the Hotel Olivia Plaza offers free Wi-Fi and a terrace bar with views of Santa Ana Church. Stylish rooms include a flat-screen TV.', 'This design hotel serves a buffet breakfast and guests can also order breakfast to the room. The modern Nineteen restaurant offers Mediterranean cuisine.', 'The chic rooms at the Olivia Hotel Barcelona include a free safe and views over the square. They are also equipped with a sofa or armchair and a breakfast table.', 'Guests at Olivia Plaza Hotel have free access to Holmes Place Urquinaona gym, located 500 m from the hotel. Guests can make free use of the pool area and fitness room there.', 'The Olivia Plaza Barcelona is just 100 m from the famous Ramblas with its many restaurants and street performers. Catalunya Metro Station is 2 minutes’ walk from the hotel and the Gothic Quarter is less than 10 minutes away.']

name: HCC Lugano
address: Avenida Paral.lel, 172, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Set on Avinguda Parallel, HCC Lugano is just over a quarter mile from Plaza España’s FIRA Exhibition Centre, and the nearby Metro and train stations. It features a 24-hour front desk and free Wi-Fi.', 'Each air-conditioned room at HCC Lugano has simple décor. There is a flat-screen TV, a minibar and a private bathroom with free toiletries.', 'Guests can enjoy a buffet breakfast in the Lugano’s cafe-bar. Restaurants can be found in Barcelona’s Gothic Quarter and along Las Ramblas, a 20-minute walk away. Drassanes Metro Station, at the bottom of Las Ramblas, is also just 2 stops from Poble Sec Metro Station.', 'Montjuïc Park, the MNAC Museum and Pueblo Español Village are less than half a kilometer from the hotel. The city’s old port is just one kilometer away.']

name: The White Flats Les Corts
address: Galileu, 316-318, Les Corts, 08028 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at The White Flats Les Corts! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Just 2 minutes’ walk from Les Corts Metro Station, The White Flats offers chic apartments in Barcelona’s financial district. They are within 10 minutes’ walk of FC Barcelona’s Camp Nou Stadium.', 'This spacious apartments with air conditioning in the living room and fan in the bedrooms.feature contemporary white décor with modern finishes. The living area has a sofa and a flat-screen TV, while the kitchen comes with a Nespresso coffee maker, a fridge, microwave, oven and a washing machine. Free Wi-Fi is available.', 'Shops, bars and cafés can be found in the surrounding area. L’Illa Shopping Center is 10 minutes’ walk away.', 'Les Corts Metro Station connects you to central Barcelona, Plaza de Catalunya and Las Ramblas in 15 minutes. Sants Railway Station and the AVE High-Speed Railway are just 2 stops away.']

name: Onix Rambla
address: Rambla Cataluña, 24, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This central Barcelona hotel is surrounded by the boutiques and cafes of the elegant Rambla de Catalunya. It offers free internet access and an outdoor pool, not heated and is open from April to October.', 'Onix Rambla has a fitness center and a business center with free internet access. There is also a nice terrace.', 'All air-conditioned rooms have flat-screen satellite TV. Rooms are also heated and come with a mini-bar and free safe. The private bathroom is equipped with a hairdryer and amenities.', 'The hotel is housed in a building with characteristic Modernist architecture. The surrounding area of the Eixample neighborhood is famous for its beautiful buildings.', 'There is a 24-hour front desk, and you can hire a car at the hotel tour desk.', '']

name: Hostal Benidorm
address: Rambla dels Caputxins, 37, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['On Barcelona’s famous Las Ramblas, the Hostal Benidorm provides free Wi-Fi, a 24-hour front desk and air-conditioned rooms with satellite TV. The Liceu Metro Station is just 197 m away.', 'Each room at the Benidorm Hostal features simple décor and tile floors. All rooms have central heating and a private bathroom.', 'Drinks and snacks are available from vending machines in the Benidorm’s lobby area. The staff at the front desk can provide information about the city and arrange car or bike rental.', 'The Hostal Benidorm is located just outside the historic Gothic Quarter. Gaudi’s Palau Güell is 100 m away, and the Boqueria Market is within a quarter mile. Barceloneta Beach can be reached in a 25-minute walk or a 10-minute bus ride.']

name: Hotel Via Augusta
address: Vía Augusta, 63, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08006 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Situated next to Gràcia FGC Train Station, Hotel Via Augusta has a rooftop terrace with views of Barcelona. They include a work desk, a safe and a bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'A varied breakfast buffet is served in the hotel, and drinks are available from the vending machine. A wide range of bars and restaurants can be found in the popular Gràcia district, within a 5-minute walk.', 'Hotel Via Augusta is 397 m from Fontana Metro Station, and Parc Güell is just 1 Metro stop away. Plaza Catalunya and Las Ramblas are a 5-minute ride from nearby Gracia Station.']
