name: Sunotel Aston
address: Paris, 101, Eixample, 08029 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Featuring a rooftop terrace with a seasonal swimming pool and hot tub, as well as panoramic views of Barcelona, Sunotel Aston is a 3-minute walk from Hospital Clinic Metro Station.', 'Air-conditioned rooms include a flat-screen TV, soundproofed windows and a private bathroom with a hairdryer. Free, high-speed WiFi is available.', 'An extensive buffet breakfast is served at the hotel. The hotel’s Maya Restaurant offers a wide selection of dishes from around the world. There are also many eating options in the area.', 'Sunotel Aston has a 24-hour reception and offers services such as luggage storage, free pool towels and free bikes.', 'Plaza Catalunya and the Ramblas can be reached in around 15 minutes by public transport; while Barcelona’s famous Sagrada Familia Cathedral is around 10 minutes away.']

name: Hotel Market
address: Comte Borrell , 68, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["Hotel Market is located next to Barcelona’s San Antonio Market, 10 minutes' walk from MACBA Gallery. Its chic rooms have rain showers and free Wi-Fi, and there is a popular restaurant.", 'The Market Hotel’s modern rooms have dark wood beams, white walls and large windows. Each one has a private bathroom. Some rooms have a balcony or terrace.', 'The hotel is 15 minutes’ walk from both Plaza Espanya and Plaza Catalunya. name: Generator Barcelona
address: Còrsega 377, Gràcia, 08037 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Generator Barcelona is located 500 m from the fashionable Passeig de Gracia Avenue. The hostel offers a 24-hour reception, free private lockers in shared dormitories and free Wi-Fi in public areas.', 'Diagonal and Verdaguer metro stations are within 5 minutes’ walk from Generator Barcelona. The Gràcia district, which has plenty of boutique shops and bars, is only 200 m away.', 'Both private rooms and dormitories have air conditioning and heating, as well as individual power sockets and reading lamps for each bed. Female-only dormitories include hairdryers and other amenities.', 'They also feature an private bathroom, a sink and a mirror. Bed linen is included, while towels can be rented at the reception. Dormitories are available for guests over 18 years old.', 'Guests can have a daily breakfast for an extra cost. Generator Barcelona also has a communal lounge and a luggage storage service.']

name: Oriente Atiram
address: Ramblas, 45, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['The Atiram Oriente is located on Las Ramblas, between the Liceu Theater and the Columbus Monument. Set in a 19th-century building, this hotel features a restaurant, terrace and free Wi-Fi.', 'All rooms have satellite TV and an private bathroom with a hairdryer. Each has simple, contemporary décor with heating and air conditioning.', 'The hotel’s pretty restaurant serves buffet cuisine and a daily continental breakfast. There is a 24-hour reception and a tour desk. The Atiram Oriente Barcelona also has a café on the Ramblas, close to many shops and restaurants.', 'The famous Boquería Market and Gothic Quarter are just a few minutes’ walk from the Hotel Atiram Oriente. Barcelona’s Port Vell is less than 500 m away and Liceu Metro Station is 5 minutes’ walk from the hotel.']

name: Aspasios Plaza Real Apartments
address: Ferran, 7, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Just off the famous Las Ramblas, Aspasios Plaza Real Apartments offers air-conditioned studios with balconies overlooking the street. La Boqueria Market and Liceu Opera House are a 2-minute walk away.', 'Each studio has smart wooden floors and functional décor. Studios are divided into a sleeping area and a living-dining area with a TV and DVD player. Free WiFi and International channels are available in all apartments.', 'You can prepare meals in the well-equipped kitchenette, which features an oven, hob, kettle and microwave. There is also a dishwasher and a washer.', 'Aspasios Plaza Real Apartments is ideally located in the Gothic Quarter, next to lively Plaça Reial Square. Barcelona Cathedral and the town hall are a 5-minute walk away. Liceu Metro Station is 150 m away.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Cosmo Apartments Passeig de Gràcia! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Cosmo Apartments Passeig de Gràcia is located in central Barcelona, 50 m from the well-know Passeig de Gràcia Avenue. Passeig de Gràcia is known for being the most important shopping street in Barcelona. Airport busses leave from Plaza Catalunya, located just 10 minutes' walk away."]

name: Praktik Vinoteca
address: Balmes, 51, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['In the heart of Barcelona, less than half a kilometer from Plaza Catalunya, Praktik Vinoteca hotel offers air-conditioned rooms and free Wi-Fi in public areas. Universitat Metro Station is a 7-minute walk away.', 'The bright and soundproof rooms at Praktik Vinoteca feature hardwood floors, a flat-screen satellite TV, telephone and a wardrobe. The private bathroom provides free toiletries and a hairdryer.', 'The property has a terrace where you can enjoy a glass of wine served by the on-site wine expert, who can tell you about local wines and their history.', 'There are bars, restaurants and supermarkets in the surrounding streets. Paseo de Gracia, with its shops and impressive architecture, is less than half a kilometer away.', 'Barcelona Airport is a 45-minute bus ride from Plaza Catalunya and Barceloneta Beach is 3.2 km from Praktik Vinoteca.']

name: Olivia Balmes Hotel
address: Balmes, 117, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Featuring an outdoor swimming pool, Olivia Balmes Hotel is a quarter mile from Barcelona’s Passeig de Gracia, in the elegant Eixample neighborhood. The modern hotel features stylish air-conditioned rooms and a restaurant.', 'Each bright spacious room includes free Wi-Fi, a flat-screen satellite TV and a laptop safe. The contemporary bathrooms have an open-plan design.', 'The hotel’s restaurant serves breakfast, lunch and dinner. Olivia Balmes has a terrace with an outdoor swimming pool and lounge chairs. There is also a bar, serving cocktails and snacks, as well as several meeting rooms.', 'Olivia Balmes Hotel has private parking, and Barcelona Airport is around a 20-minute drive from the hotel. Plaza Catalunya is a 15-minute walk from the hotel, and Gaudi’s famous Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are within a 5-minute walk of the hotel.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel Condal! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set 50 m from Las Ramblas and Liceu Metro Station, Hotel Condal offers rooms with free WiFi and private bathrooms. Opened in 1850, this hotel in Barcelona’s Gothic Quarter offers air conditioned or heated accommodations, depending on the season.', 'The Condal’s rooms have simple décor with tiled floors. Each room has a flat-screen TV.', 'A continental breakfast is served in Hotel Condal’s café-bar. There is a varied selection of restaurants in the streets surrounding the hotel.', 'Staff at the 24-hour reception can provide information on Barcelona’s many attractions, including the MACBA Museum and Barcelona Cathedral, which can be reached in 10 minutes by foot. The Condal is less than 0.6 mi from Port Vell Marina.']

name: Ola Living Portaferrissa
address: Petrixol, 17, Ciutat Vella, 08003 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Ola Living Portaferrissa! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Centrally located, Ola Living Portaferrissa offers air-conditioned apartments and studios with free Wi-Fi and free safe. Accommodations are 100 m from Ramblas and Plaza Catalunya is 5 minutes’ walk away.', 'Featuring modern and functional furniture each accommodations comes with a flat-screen cable TV, DVD player and a fully equipped kitchenette including a coffee machine, microwave and oven. A washing machine, clothes dryer and iron facilities are also provided.', 'Ola Living Portaferrissa is surrounded by a wide range of bars, restaurant and traditional Spanish Granjas for a snack or a light meal. You can find fresh produce in La Boquería Market, 200 m away.', 'You can walk to the Cathedral in 5 minutes from Ola Living Portaferrissa. Lively Plaza Reial is 400 m away and Barcelona Museum of Contemporary Art is 7 minutes’ walk from accommodations. The closest metro station is Liceu, just 300 m away.']

name: Hotel Serhs del Port
address: Avenida Paralelo, 40, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Set on Paral-lel Avenue, this modern design hotel is just a 5-minute walk from the famous Las Ramblas and Barcelona Port. Its stylish, air-conditioned rooms feature free WiFi and a satellite TV.', 'Hotel Serhs del Port´s modern rooms offer a safe. The private bathrooms come with a hairdryer and free toiletries.', 'Montjuïc Hill is within a 10-minute walk of Hotel Serhs del Port. A funicular train connects Montjuïc with Paral-lel Metro Station, located 500 m from the hotel.', 'Direct Metro services also connect Paral-lel to Plaça Catalunya Square, Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard and Gaudí’s famous Parc Guëll. Hotel Serhs del Port´s tour desk can provide information about the city.']

name: Aparthotel Allada 3*
address: Allada i Vermell, 6-8, Ciutat Vella, 08003 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in a pedestrianized street in the neighborhood of Borne, Aparthotel Allada 3* offers a tranquil atmosphere due to the scarcity of street noise and the sound-proofing of the building.', 'Aparthotel Allada 3* is located in a picturesque, historical area that has maintained the façades and arches of the 17th century, while incorporating the modern architecture of the 21st century. The apartments and studios have been designed to offer the greatest comfort and functionality during your stay. All also benefit from ample natural light throughout the day.', 'The Borne district is full of winding streets that form a labyrinth, allowing you to find some of the most intriguing areas in the old city. Close to the apartments, you will find the church of Saint Mary, the city gardens, the Picasso museum, the chocolate museum, the Cathedral, the market of Saint Catherine as well as many other sites of interest. In addition, you enjoy free access to the Barcelona Egyptian Museum.']

name: Gran Hotel Havana 4* Sup
address: Gran Vía de Les Corts Catalanes, 647, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This elegant, design hotel is set in Barcelona’s city center, 5 minutes’ walk from Plaza Catalunya. It features a sauna and a seasonal rooftop pool with a terrace.', 'The Gran Hotel Havana is located in Casa Fradera, a historic building dating from 1882. Rooms are decorated in a classic style and feature a marble bathroom. They come with a flat-screen TV and free WiFi.', 'The Grand Place restaurant serves traditional cuisine, and in summer guests can enjoy light meals on the hotel’s rooftop bar-terrace.', 'Please note that the rooftop bar-terrace may be closed to the public at certain times due to private events.', 'Girona Metro Station is 200 m away while the stylish Paseo de Gracia is just 5 minutes’ walk from the hotel, with many shops, bars and restaurants.']

name: Charmsuites Nou Rambla
address: Nou de la Rambla, 114-116, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Set just off Avinguda Paral.lel, Charmsuites Nou Rambla offers bright, stylish apartments with free Wi-Fi. Paral·lel Metro and Funicular Station is within 100 m of the property.', 'Each spacious apartment at Charmsuites Nou Rambla has a living area with a flat-screen TV and a DVD player. There is a dining area, and a kitchen with an electric hob, oven, coffee maker and fridge.', 'Shops can be found in the streets surrounding the hotel. There are many cafés, bars and restaurants in the nearby Raval district and on Las Ramblas, a 10-minute walk away.', 'Barcelona’s Old Port is less than 0.6 mi from the apartments. Plaza España Square, the Fira Exhibition Center and Sants Railway Station can be reached in 10 minutes by Metro.']

name: Fisa Rentals Ramblas Apartments
address: Pelai, 11, Eixample, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Fisa Rentals Ramblas Apartments is located in central Barcelona, just 250 m from Plaza Catalunya and the Ramblas. It offers stylish, air-conditioned apartments with free Wi-Fi and flat-screen satellite TV.', 'The Fisa Rentals apartments feature parquet floors and modern décor. Each one comes with a DVD player, and the kitchen includes a hob, microwave, washing machine and dishwasher.', 'Gaudí’s Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are about 15 minutes’ walk from the apartments. La Boquería Market and the spectacular Palau de la Música Catalana are within a 10-minute walk. Airport buses leave from Plaza Catalunya.']

name: Hotel & Spa Villa Olimpica Suites
address: Pallars, 121-125, Sant Martí, 08018 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This minimalist hotel is located in the Poble Nou district of Barcelona, 15 minutes’ by foot from Bogatell Beach. It offers a seasonal outdoor pool surrounded by attractive wooden decking and loungers.', 'The chic suites at Hotel & Spa Villa Olimpic@ feature monochrome decoration and a flat-screen TV. They also include air conditioning and a modern bathroom.', 'The Hotel & Spa Villa Olimpic@ Suites complex offers a stylish café-bar and restaurant. Guests can enjoy Mediterranean cuisine from the á la carte and daily menus. In summer meals can be enjoyed on the terrace by the pool.', "Guests have access to the hotel's large spa for an additional cost. It includes an indoor treatment pool, Finnish sauna, Turkish baths, hot tubs, several types of shower and an ice fountain. There is also a gym.", "Barcelona Port is 15 minutes' walk away and Bogatell Metro Station is 100 m from the hotel. Guests can walk to the lively Villa Olimpica area in 5 minutes.", 'All rooms include 1 complimentary access per person per stay to the hotel spa (subject to availability and upon reservation).']

name: Hostel New York
address: Gignas, 6-8, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hostel New York is a youth hostel located in Barcelona’s Gothic Quarter, 5 minutes’ walk from Las Ramblas. It offers 24-hour reception and free WiFi, 500 m from Jaume and Drassanes Metro Stations.', 'The hostel’s simple dormitory rooms feature modest décor, bunk beds and individual lockers. They include access to a shared bathroom; and free bed linen are provided.', 'There is a kitchen available for guests in the evenings and a TV lounge with vending machines selling drinks and snacks. There are also 2 computers.', "New York is ideally located for visiting many of Barcelona’s sights by foot. Ciutadella Park is a 10-minute walk away and Barceloneta Beach is 15 minutes's walk away.", '']

name: Hotel Astoria
address: Paris, 203, Eixample, 08036 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Astoria is just off Barcelona’s Diagonal Avenue, a 5-minute walk from Diagonal Metro Station and Paseo de Gracia Avenue. It features a rooftop pool with views, and a gym.', 'The Astoria Hotel combines original Art Nouveau features with modern facilities. Air-conditioned rooms have satellite TV, a safe and mini-bar. They feature wooden floors and free Wi-Fi, and the modern bathrooms come with a hairdryer.', 'The restaurant at the Astoria offers traditional Catalan cuisine, and room service is available. There is also a terrace and a bar.', 'There is a 24-hour front desk and you can hire a car.']

name: Catalonia Atenas
address: Avenida Meridiana, 151, Sant Martí, 08026 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Atenas! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set 3 metro stops from central Barcelona, the Atenas Catalonia has a rooftop swimming pool, offering views of the nearby Torre Agbar and Sagrada Familia. It also features free WiFi, a gym and a spa with a Turkish bath.', 'The bright rooms of Hotel Atenas Barcelona have simple décor with wooden flooring. Each has air conditioning, a mini fridge with complimentary water, and satellite TV.', "The hotel's buffet breakfast features a show kitchen. There is a snack bar and guests can enjoy stunning city views from the pool, set on the 11th floor.", 'The Sagrada Familia is just over one kilometer from the hotel, while Glòries shopping center can be reached in 15 minutes by foot.', 'The Catalonia Atenas has a convenient left luggage service, on-site parking, and is 2 minutes’ walk from Clot Metro Station; and 200 m from Clot Train Station; here you can take a direct train to Barcelona Airport.']

name: Sunotel Junior
address: Avenida Sarrià, 9, Eixample, 08029 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Offering panoramic views from its rooftop terrace, which has a seasonal hot tub and swimming pool, Sunotel Junior is set 300 m from Francesc Macià Square. It offers free, high-speed WiFi.', 'All rooms at Sunotel Junior have air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, soundproofed windows and a fully equipped bathroom.', 'Guests can enjoy a varied buffet breakfast each morning. The hotel’s restaurant, Maya, offers a selection of dishes from around the world. There is also a range of cafés and restaurants nearby.', 'You will find a 24-hour reception that offers a luggage storage service and free pool towels. There are also several meeting rooms available.', 'The Sunotel is a 5-minute walk from Hospital Clinic Metro Station, and Sants Railway Station is just 2 metro stops away.', 'FC Barcelona’s famous Camp Nou Stadium can be reached in 15 minutes by public transport, and Plaza de Catalunya and Las Ramblas are also around 15 minutes away.']

Ciutadela Park is a 10-minute walk away.']

name: Acta Atrium Palace
address: Gran Via Corts Catalanes, 656, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This elegant hotel is 250 m from Paseo de Gracia Metro Station and Boulevard. Plaza Catalunya is a 5-minute walk away. It offers free Wi-Fi.', 'Set in an attractive building, dating from 1888, rooms at the Acta Atrium Palace are modern and chic, with air conditioning and satellite TV. The private bathrooms offer free toiletries and a bathrobe.', 'The hotel has 24-hour room service.', "Gaudí's famous Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are 10 minutes' walk away. There is a 24-hour front desk, and you can hire a car at the hotel tour desk. Public parking is available nearby."]

name: Cosmo Apartments Marina – Auditori
address: Ausias Marc, 136, Eixample, 08013 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Cosmo Apartments Marina – Auditori! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'The bright, stylish Cosmo Apartments Marina – Auditori are located 200 m from Monumental Bullring and Metro Station. Free WiFi is available.', 'Cosmo Apartments Marina – Auditori modern, air-conditioned apartments have flat-screen TVs. They feature wooden floors and chic décor throughout.', 'All accommodations includes a living room and dining area. The open plan kitchens are equipped with a fridge, dishwasher, microwave, a washer-dryer machine, kettle, and a coffee machine. Some apartments have a DVD player and an extra TV in the bedrooms. All come with private bathroom. Bed linen, towels and kitchenware are provided.', 'Glories Shopping Center, the Encants flea market, and Razzmatazz concert hall are 500 m from the apartments. The center of Barcelona is just 3 Metro stops away. There are regular bus connections nearby, which connect guests to the city’s beaches in 15 minutes.', 'The apartments are 100 m from the Auditori and the National Theater, and 200 m from Agbar Tower and the Nord Bus Station.']

name: C211 Barcelona Apartments
address: Casanova, 211, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08021 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at C211 Barcelona Apartments! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Stylish, modern apartments include free Wi-Fi, air conditioning and views of Barcelona. Located just off Diagonal Avenue, C211 Barcelona is 15 minutes’ walk from Passeig de Gracia.', 'Each apartment includes a lounge with sofas, a flat-screen TV, DVD player and an iPad docking station. Their kitchens are equipped with an oven, microwave and washing machine; bed linen and towels are provided. Some also feature a balcony or terrace.', 'Many shops, restaurants and bars can be found in the surrounding streets. The local Galvany Market is a 5-minute walk from the apartments.', 'Both Hospital Clinic and Diagonal metro stations are under 15 minutes’ walk away and connect with Sants Train Station and the rest of the city.']

name: Sixties Ramblas
address: Passatge Gutenberg, 7, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Sixties Ramblas! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Offering a 1960’s vibe and rooms with vintage décor, this hotel is set in the heart of Barcelona, only 2 minutes’ walk from the famous Ramblas. Free Wi-Fi is available throughout.', 'Each air-conditioned room at Sixties Ramblas features a TV and a private bathroom. Most rooms have a balcony.', 'Sixties Ramblas has a bar and a restaurant. Staff at the 24-hour reception can provide tourist information about the area. Bike rental services are also available, and there is also a stylish white billiards table.', 'The nearest Metro Station is Drassanes, only 2 minutes’ walk from the hotel. You can also walk to the harbor or Plaza Catalunya Square in less than 10 minutes.', 'Sixties Ramblas is close to the Born district, with numerous trendy bars and restaurants serving local and international food.']

Barcelona FC’s Camp Nou Stadium is just one metro stop away.']

name: AinB Eixample-Miro Apartments
address: Entença, 140, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at AinB Eixample-Miro Apartments! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'These stylish and comfortable apartments are in Barcelona’s chic Eixample district, just over a quarter mile from Gran Vía. They feature a balcony, air conditioning and free Wi-Fi, a 10-minute walk from Plaza España.', 'Apartments in Barcelona Eixample-Miro have chic decor and plenty of natural light. Lounges have a sofa bed and plasma TV and modern kitchens include a coffee machine, microwave, stove and oven.', 'There are various bars, restaurants and shops within a 5-minute walk of the property. The Las Arenas Shopping Center is a 10-minute walk away.', 'The foot of Montjuic hill, with the Olympic Stadium, MNAC and Caixa Forum Museums, is a 10-minute walk away and the Joan Miró Park is a 4-minute walk away.', 'The Eixample-Miro apartments are a 5-minute walk from Entença and Tarragona Metro Stations, connecting you with Las Ramblas in 10 minutes. Sants AVE Train Station is less than half a kilometer away.']

name: Gallery Hotel
address: Rosselló, 249, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located just off Barcelona’s Passeig de Gracia, Gallery Hotel offers a free sauna and gym, and a seasonal rooftop terrace with a pool and city views. Rooms include free Wi-Fi and free water on arrival.', 'This elegant hotel offers spacious, air-conditioned rooms with flat-screen satellite TV. The modern bathrooms include amenities, a hairdryer and a bathrobe.', 'The Gallery’s restaurant has an attractive garden terrace where you can enjoy Mediterranean cuisine, including a weekend gourmet menu. The hotel also has a bar and a café.', 'Gallery Hotel is located next to the gardens of Palau Robert, a gallery and tourist information center. Gaudí’s La Pedrera is a 3-minute walk away, while nearby Diagonal Metro Station provides direct access to the Sagrada Familia. Regular airport trains stop 601 m away at Passeig de Gracia Station.']

name: Citadines Ramblas Barcelona
address: Las Ramblas, 122, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Centrally located on Barcelona’s famous Las Ramblas Boulevard, this aparthotel offers 24-hour reception and is surrounded by many restaurants, bars and shops. Free WiFi is available throughout the property.', 'All air-conditioned studios and apartments at Citadines Ramblas Barcelona feature a kitchen with a microwave, fridge and dishwasher. Bathrooms are equipped with hairdryers and all rooms have a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. All Classic Rooms are equipped with fridge and kettle.', 'Linen and towels are provided. The apartment is cleaned and linen and towels are changed for free once a week. An additional housecleaning service is available upon request and is charged according to your needs.', 'Bicycle and car rental can be arranged for guests at Citadines. Luggage storage is also available and the aparthotel operates a ticket service for attractions in Barcelona.', 'Plaza Catalunya Metro Station is just 100 m away, and airport busses leave from the square. The impressive Boqueria Market is 2 minutes’ walk from Citadines Ramblas.']

name: Bonanova Park
address: Capità Arenas, 51, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08034 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This family-run hotel is located 701 m from the Politècnica de Catalunya University and Palau Reial Gardens. Bonanova Park offers air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi and flat-screen satellite TV.', 'Each room at the Bonanova Park has a simple, functional design. Rooms come with a CD player, mini-bar (drinks and snacks not included) and private bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'A varied buffet breakfast served in the Bonanova Park’s breakfast room. There are also numerous bars and restaurants in the charming Sarria neighborhood, a 10-minute walk away.', 'Hotel Bonanova Park is around 0.6 mi from L’Illa Diagonal Shopping Center, and a 15-minute walk from FC Barcelona’s Camp Nou Stadium. Maria Cristina Metro Station is 500 m away, and offers direct links to the city center and to the Palau de Congressos Conference Center, 2 stops away.', 'Private parking can be found near the hotel.']

name: The Moods Oasis
address: 72 Travessera de Gràcia, Sarrià-St. Gervasi, 08006 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Ideally located in the Sarrià-St. Gervasi district of Barcelona, The Moods Oasis is located a 12-minute walk from La Pedrera, 1.4 km from Casa Batllo and 1.9 km from Passeig de Gracia. This 3-star hotel offers a concierge service and a tour desk. The hotel has a fitness center, a 24-hour front desk and free WiFi throughout the property.', 'The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower. At The Moods Oasis the rooms have bed linen and towels.', 'Guests at the accommodation can enjoy a continental or a buffet breakfast.', 'The Moods Oasis has a terrace.', 'The hotel provides an ironing service, as well as business facilities like fax and photocopying.', 'Passeig de Gracia Metro Station is 1.8 km from The Moods Oasis, while Plaça Catalunya is 2.1 km from the property. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 16.1 km from the accommodation.']

name: HCC Regente
address: Rambla de Catalunya, 76, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hotel HCC Regente is set in a traditional Modernist building which has been recently restored, maintaining its original features. HCC Regente is located on Rambla de Catalunya.', 'The Regente features Art Nouveau décor and wrought-iron balconies. Each air-conditioned room has satellite TV, free wired internet access and a mini-bar.', 'The hotel serves a varied breakfast in its restaurant. There is a wide range of cafés, bars and restaurants in the streets surrounding the HCC.', 'Attractions including Las Ramblas and Gaudí’s Casa Batlló are within 10 minutes’ walk of the Regente. Passeig de Gràcia Metro Station is just 200 m from the hotel.']

name: Best Western Premier Hotel Dante
address: Mallorca, 181, Eixample, 08036 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['The Best Western Premier Dante is located in the Eixample district of Barcelona, a few minutes walking from the elegant Paseo de Gracia, Plaza de Catalunya and the famous Pedrera and Casa Batlló. With a functional design, the Hotel has a Lobby Bar, meeting rooms, internet corner and private parking.', 'The rooms are spacious and daylight. They have free WI-FI connection, coffee maker, electronic safe, LCD satellite TV and air conditioning, as well as a complete bathroom. The Suites are located on the 7th floor and have a large terrace with views of Barcelona.', "The Buffet Breakfast offers a wide variety of milk and vegetable drinks, juices, coffees, infusions, pastries and salty. Many of the products served are gluten free. The Hotel's Lobby Bar, serves Mediterranean cuisine, both for lunch and dinner. It is also possible to taste an aperitif.\nThe Hotel also has 4 fully equipped meeting rooms and private parking, as well as free Wi-Fi in rooms and common areas.", 'It is about 20 minutes away by car from Barcelona airport and 10 from the AVE station.']

name: Leonardo Hotel Barcelona Las Ramblas
address: Junta de Comercio, 8,10,12, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Leonardo Hotel Barcelona Las Ramblas is located in the center of Barcelona’s Old Town, just 200 m from Las Ramblas. It features a rooftop terrace with a seasonal swimming pool.', 'The hotel offers simple, attractive décor and rooms are spacious. Each has air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, as well as tea and coffee making facilities.', 'The Leonardo Hotel Barcelona Las Ramblas serves a daily, buffet breakfast. There are several bars, cafés and restaurants within walking distance of the property.', 'Guests can make use of computers with internet access, available in the hotel reception area. Staff at the tour desk can provide information on Barcelona’s tourist attractions and arrange car rental.', 'The hotel is 10 minutes’ walk from Barcelona Cathedral and the city’s Gothic Quarter. The Old Port is around 701 m from the hotel, while Liceu Metro is a 10-minute walk away.']

By direct metro you can reach La Rambla in 15 minutes.", 'The Tibidabo Apartments are set within an old villa with a spacious garden and terrace.', "The location is convenient for access by car, with the Ronda de Dalt (B20 Ring Road) 200 m away. name: Catalonia Passeig de Gràcia 4* Sup
address: Gran Via de les Corts Catalanes, 644, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Passeig de Gràcia 4* Sup! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Catalonia Passeig de Gràcia is located next to Barcelona’s Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard. This modern hotel offers an outdoor pool, a free gym and stylish rooms with free Wi-Fi.', 'Set in a classic-style building dating from 1928, Catalonia Passeig de Gràcia has modern interiors. The air-conditioned rooms include wine service from 13:00 to 20:00 and a Nespresso coffee machine. Some rooms have a private terrace.', 'At the restaurant Les Delícies you can taste Mediterranean cuisine with a selection of dishes from the "Gourmet Corner" menu from Monday to Sunday. The restaurant has a terrace for smokers. Gluten-free menus are also available on request. There is also a gastrobar and a bar with a cocktail menu.', 'Gaudí’s Casa Batlló is 500 m from the hotel, and you can walk to La Pedrera in 13 minutes. The impressive Palau de la Música Catalana is 7 minutes’ walk away.', 'Catalonia Passeig de Gràcia offers private on-site parking for an extra cost as well as an electric vehicle charging station. Passeig de Gràcia Metro Station is just 200 m away. Airport buses leave from Plaza Catalunya, located 350 m away.']

address: Sant Pau, 22, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Dalia Ramblas! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set 50 m from the Ramblas, in the Raval district, Dalia Ramblas features air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi. Well served by public transport, it offers 24-hour reception and free luggage storage.', 'Featuring a modern and functional décor, rooms come with a flat-screen TV, wardrobe and a desk. All have a private bathroom with bath or shower. Free toiletries and hairdryer are provided.', 'Dalia Ramblas is set in the lively city center. name: Vincci Gala
address: Ronda Sant Pere, 32, Eixample, 08010 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Vincci Gala! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'In the heart of Barcelona, Vincci Gala hotel offers luxurious rooms in a protected 19th-century palace. Free Wi-Fi is available.', 'The orginal façade, floor and central staircase of this unique hotel have all been preserved, creating a balance of traditional arquitecture and modern design.', 'The air-conditioned rooms include a private bathroom with hairdryer, free toiletries, and bathtub or shower. The rooms also have a free laptop safe, extra large beds, satellite TV with pay-per-view channels, and a minibar.', 'A restaurant and snack bar are available on-site, and the hotel offers a breakfast buffet. Laundry and car rental services are available for a fee, and the property can provide tourist information.', "Vincci Gala hotel is located across from Urquinaona Metro Station, a 2-minute walk from Plaça Catalunya Square. There are many bars, restaurants and shops in the surroundings, and you can reach Gaudi's La Sagrada Familia in 15 minutes by metro."]

name: BCN Urbaness Hotels Del Comte
address: Diputació, 142, Eixample, 08015 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["Hotel Del Comte is 100 m from Barcelona's Urgell Metro Station and 15 minutes walk from the Rambla and Plaza Espanya. It offers modern rooms with free Wi-Fi and a flat-screen TV with satellite channels.", 'The air-conditioned rooms at Del Comte feature parquet floors and smart design. Each one comes with a work desk and a private bathroom with a hairdryer.', 'Staff at the Del Comte Hotel’s 24-hour reception can provide information about what to see and do in Barcelona.', 'There is a bus stop just 3 minutes’ walk from the Del Comte which provides transport connections to Barcelona El Prat Airport. It is only 2 stops on the Metro to Plaza Catalunya, Barcelona’s main square.']

name: Hotel Granados 83, a Member of Design Hotels
address: Enrique Granados, 83, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located 250 m from Barcelona’s Diagonal Metro Station, Granados 83 offers a small gym and roof terrace with a small pool and cocktail bar. Rooms feature Zen-style design and LCD TV.', 'This design hotel has an impressive glass and stone façade and it combines neoclassical details with industrial and natural components which has become representative of the entire city and which gives it the Specialty Monument status. It also features beautiful Art Deco interiors.', 'Decorated with wood, leather and glass, the Granados 83’s stylish air-conditioned rooms include a mini-bar, bathrobe and slippers.', 'The elegant restaurant serves creative Mediterranean cuisine and room service is available. There are many popular tapas bars within a 5-minute walk, on Rambla de Catalunya.', 'Passeig de Gràcia is 400 m away, and is home to Gaudí’s famous La Pedrera and Casa Batlló.', 'There is a 24-hour reception and free Wi-Fi throughout the hotel. You can hire a car from the tour desk, and on-site parking is offered for an extra charge.']

name: Novotel Barcelona City
address: Avenida Diagonal 201, Sant Martí, 08018 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['This hotel offers a free gym and a roof terrace with a seasonal outdoor pool and panoramic views of Barcelona. The rooms include free Wi-Fi and flat-screen satellite TV.', 'Novotel Barcelona City is located next to Glòries Shopping Center and the Glories Tower, designed by Jean Nouvel. The Sagrada Familia Basilica and Bogatell Beach are both a 20-minute walk away.', 'The air-conditioned rooms at Novotel Barcelona City have simple, modern décor. Up to 2 children under 16 stay for free when sharing with parents.', 'The hotel’s restaurant offers characteristic Mediterranean food.', 'On the rooftop there is an outdoor swimming pool and a gourmet bar where guests can enjoy tapas, wines and cocktails enjoying panoramic city views.', 'Staff at reception are happy to provide information about Barcelona. Tram and bus services to the city center stop outside the hotel. Glòries Metro Station is just 300 m away.']

name: Hotel Concordia Barcelona
address: Paral·lel, 115, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Hotel Concordia Barcelona is located 801 m from Plaza España and the Fira de Barcelona Exhibition Center. It features a sun terrace with an outdoor swimming pool, hot tub, cocktail bar and solarium.', 'The Hotel Concordia Barcelona’s bright, spacious rooms feature contemporary décor and air conditioning. Each room includes free WiFi, a flat-screen TV, safe, mini-bar and a private bathroom with a range of amenities.', 'The Concordia Barcelona’s modern, elegant Bistro Triple Sec Restaurant serves characteristic Mediterranean cuisine. The varied breakfast buffet includes healthy options. There is also a café and cocktail bar open daily. Private parking is available on site for an extra cost and electrical cars charging station is available.', 'Located next to Poble Sec Station, the hotel is a 5-minute Metro journey from Barcelona Port and La Rambla. You can also walk to the Rambla in 15 minutes. Direct airport busses stop in Plaza España, a 15-minute walk away.', 'Private parking is available on site for an extra cost.']

hotel_description: ['This hotel is next to Diagonal Mar Shopping Center and just 400 m from Nova Mar Bella Beach. It offers a seasonal outdoor pool, a fitness center and air-conditioned rooms with a LED TV.', "Hilton Diagonal Mar Barcelona's terrace, Purobeach Barcelona, has an outdoor pool and paddling pool available from April to October. All services on the Purobeach terrace, including Balinese beds, sunbeds and massages are available for an extra charge.", "Purobeach Restaurant offers a diverse menu, as well as a variety of classic cocktails and international spirits. Aürt Restaurant serves Catalan food cooked in front of you. Guests can also enjoy tapas, snacks or drinks at Ma'i.", "The hotel has 22 meeting rooms. Barcelona’s CCIB Convention Center is located next door to the hotel. El Maresme-Forum Metro Station is 2 minutes’ walk away, and from here you can get to central Barcelona in around 15 minutes. Barcelona's El Prat Airport is 25 minutes' drive away."]

name: Golden Hotel Barcelona
address: Calle Ávila, 135-139, Sant Martí, 08018 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located in Barcelona, 0.9 mi from Sagrada Familia, Golden Hotel Barcelona is a sustainable property with the Biosphere certificate. It provides a rooftop terrace with outdoor swimming pool, jacuzzi and bar. 0.9 mi from Port Olympic, the property is also 1.1 mi from Sagarda Familia and 1.2 mi away from Picasso Museum. There is a gym, a restaurant and a shared lounge.', 'All guests staying at the Golden Hotel Barcelona get 1 free entry for person and stay to the spa at Hotel & Spa Villa Olimpic@ Suites complex (subject to availability and with prior reservation), located 450 m away.', 'A buffet breakfast is available each morning at the property.', 'Speaking Spanish, Catalan, German and English at the reception, staff are ready to help around the clock.', 'Barcelona El Prat Airport is 9.3 mi from the property.']

name: Duquesa de Cardona 4* Sup
address: Passeig Colom, 12, Ciutat Vella, 08002 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['The 19th-century Duquesa de Cardona, opposite Barcelona’s marina in the Gothic Quarter, is 601 m from the Ramblas and has free Wi-Fi. Its rooftop terrace offers panoramic city views and includes 2 plunge pools and a bar. Property also features a Gym.', 'Duquesa de Cardona Hotel Barcelona has spacious, air-conditioned rooms with a flat-screen satellite TV, a safety deposit box and a mini-bar. The private bathroom comes with a bathrobe and slippers.', 'The hotel’s restaurant offers Mediterranean cuisine and has an extensive wine list, including many Spanish cavas. During summer, the snack bar serves creative tapas, BBQ dishes and cocktails.', 'The famous Sagrada Familia is 1.6 mi away, and Barceloneta Metro Station is only 300 m away. The Maremagnum Shopping Center and Barcelona Aquarium are 500 m from Duquesa de Cardona Barcelona.']

name: InterContinental Barcelona, an IHG Hotel
address: Avenida Rius y Taulet, 1-3, Sants-Montjuïc, 08004 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located 200 m from Barcelona’s Magic Fountain, the elegant InterContinental Barcelona, an IHG Hotel offers spacious rooms with a flat-screen TV and hydromassage shower.', 'Offering fantastic views over Barcelona, the hotel’s 173 Rooftop Terrace features an outdoor pool, sun loungers, and a dining area where guests can enjoy Mediterranean cuisine and a selection of drinks and cocktails.', 'Arrel Restaurant pays homage to the land and the produce it provides throughout all seasons of the year. The restaurant features an open kitchen serving small portions to share, buffet breakfasts and lunch and dinner service.', 'Quirat Restaurant is an exclusive space that will offer an interpretation of the land and its products through a menu of dishes that responds to the different seasons, designed exclusively for the restaurant by a Chef with 1 Michelin Star. Enjoy an unforgettable dinner in the most exclusive of our restaurants.', 'Gebre Cocktails and More and, in addition to the cocktail classics, it will offer a menu of artisan signature cocktails that will try to convey a very specific sensory experience connected to the world of the land that surrounds us.', 'There is free WiFi available in public areas and in rooms and the lobby area at InterContinental Barcelona, an IHG Hotel features a free internet point.', 'The spa has a water circuit, a dry sauna, a hammam, hot tub, gym, and 6 treatment cabins.', 'From the hotel, Barcelona’s historic center can be easily reached by bus or metro. Poble Sec and Espanya Metro Stations are both 500 m away. Poble Espanyol and the Joan Miró Foundation are 200 m away.']

name: Zenit Borrell
address: Comte Borrell, 208, Eixample, 08029 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Zenit Borrell is in Barcelona’s Eixample district, a 15 minute walk from the stylish Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard. It offers modern, soundproof rooms with free Wi-Fi and satellite TV.', 'The Marés restaurant offers Mediterranean and international cuisine, and has an elegant outdoor terrace. There is also a bar with a large TV screen.', 'All rooms at the Zenit Borrell have air conditioning and a minibar. The private bathrooms come equipped with a hairdryer.', 'The tour desk can provide useful information on Barcelona and the surrounding area. The hotel is 12 minutes from Plaza Catalunya and the Ramblas by metro, while the Hospital Clinic Metro Station and hospital are 202 m away from the hotel.']

name: Barceló Raval
address: Rambla del Raval, 17-21, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Barceló Raval! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set in Barcelona’s vibrant Raval district, this design hotel offers free Wi-Fi, a gym and a roof terrace with pool and panoramic views. Some rooms include a Nespresso coffee machine.', 'Each bright, air-conditioned room at the Barceló Raval features a large plasma-screen TV with more than 70 channels. Rooms have a mini-bar and a modern bathroom.', 'Hotel Barceló Raval’s B-Lounge serves creative Mediterranean food, tapas and cocktails in stylish surroundings. You can also enjoy a drink on the outdoor terrace.', 'The Raval Barceló is only a 5-minute walk from the MACBA Modern Art Gallery. Liceu Metro Station, Las Ramblas and the famous Boqueria Market are all just 400 m away.']

name: El Avenida Palace
address: Gran Via, 605, Eixample, 08007 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['El Avenida Palace Hotel is set on Barcelona’s Gran Via, 5 minutes’ walk from Plaza Catalunya, La Rambla and Paseo de Gracia. Its grand interior features an impressive staircase and marble columns.', 'Many famous guests have stayed at the Hotel Avenida Palace, including the Beatles in 1965.', 'The elegant air-conditioned rooms feature satellite TV and carpeted or parquet floors. Rooms are soundproofed and have a mini-bar, work desk and a safe.', "The hotel's panoramic rooftop terrace offers views over the city, a sun deck and a swimming pool. There is also a lounge bar, a 24-hour front desk and both free WiFi and room service are available."]

name: Hotel Best Auto Hogar
address: Avenida Paral.lel, 64, Ciutat Vella, 08001 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hotel Best Auto Hogar! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Set on Parallel Avenue, the Hotel Auto Hogar is right across from Parallel Metro Station and a 10-minute walk from the Ramblas. It includes air-conditioned rooms with private bathrooms.', 'All rooms have a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. The private bathroom includes a hairdryer and vanity mirror.', 'Some of Barcelona’s most popular theaters can be found within a 5-minute walk, and Montjuïc hill is a 15-minute walk from the hotel. The Fira Exhibition Centre is just over half a kilometer away.', 'The Auto Hogar Hotel’s restaurant serves Mediterranean dishes, and is open 7 days a week. The hotel also has a café.', 'The hotel front desk provides free newspapers, and can arrange bike and car rental.']

name: Occidental Atenea Mar - Adults Only
address: Paseo García Faria, 37-47, Sant Martí, 08019 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Located 150 m from Barcelona’s Nova Mar Bella Beach, Occidental Atenea Mar - Adults Only offers sauna and gym, and a free WiFi zone. Each air-conditioned room features international satellite TV.', 'The hotel features a terrace with sea views and a seasonal infinity pool with hydromassage beds and seats. You can rent Balinese beds and sun loungers. There is also a seasonal snack bar, which is open from June to September.', 'Occidental Atenea Mar - Adults Only offers bright, functional rooms, many with views of the city or sea. They include a mini-bar, a free safe and a private bathroom with amenities.', 'The hotel’s Canela restaurant serves à la carte Mediterranean meals, and a varied breakfast buffet is available each morning. There are also many bars and restaurants on the nearby seafront promenade.', 'Regular bus services to central Barcelona stop outside the Occidental Atenea Mar - Adults Only, while Poble Nou Metro Station is a 10-minute walk away. The CCIB Conference Center and Diagonal Mar Shopping Center are just 0.6 mi from the hotel.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Paral·lel! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Situated just a 10-minutes walk from the stunning center of Barcelona, this stylish and practical hotel is set in the charming neighborhood of Poble Sec, at the foot of Montjüic, where you can visit the Olympic site.', 'Start your day with breakfast in Paral.lel, before heading out for a stroll up Montjüic, where you can spend the day relaxing in a natural setting, and also visit museums such as Fundació Joan Mirò and the national gallery, MNAC.', 'Each of the bedrooms in Paral.lel comes with air conditioning, so you can enjoy tranquility and rest in the warm summer months. Browse the internet using the free Wi-Fi connection available in this hotel.', 'Paral.lel is located just a short stroll from the port and beach area of the city, and you can get to top sights such as Las Ramblas and the Gothic Quarter with its stunning cathedral.']

name: Hotel Balmes
address: Mallorca, 216, Eixample, 08008 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ['Balmes is located in central Barcelona, 5 minutes’ walk from the famous Passeig de Gràcia Boulevard. It offers a swimming pool, a gym/fitness center and modern rooms with satellite TV.', 'The air-conditioned rooms at Hotel Balmes feature parquet floors and smart, simple décor. They all come with a private bathroom, a flat-screen TV and free Wi-Fi.', 'The hotel’s restaurant serves characteristic Catalan food using fresh market produce. B Bar, like the rest of the hotel, is decorated with works of African art.', 'Staff at the hotel’s 24-hour reception can help booking tickets for guided tours, live shows and other events. There is a computer in the lobby which guests can use for free.', 'Gaudí’s Casa Batlló and La Pedrera are both under 10 minutes’ walk from the hotel. You can walk to Las Ramblas and Barcelona’s charming Gothic Quarter in around 15 minutes.']

name: Chic & Basic Born Boutique Hotel
address: Princesa, 50, Ciutat Vella, 08003 Barcelona, Spain
hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Chic & Basic Born Boutique Hotel! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'This design hotel is in Barcelona’s trendy Born district, 250 m from the Picasso Museum. It features a gym, 24-hour reception, and air-conditioned rooms with colorful LED lighting and flat-screen TVs.', 'Free coffee, tea and water are offered in a self-service area in the Chic & Basic Born. The hotel also has a lounge with free Wi-Fi and comfortable designer armchairs.', 'The Modernist-style building has high ceilings, large windows and marble staircases. It is within 100 m of Ciudadela Park and Barcelona’s Chocolate Museum. La Rambla is a 10-minute walk away.', 'Rooms at the Chic & Basic Born Boutique Hotel feature a glass shower cubicle in the center of the room. There is also a hairdryer, slippers and bathroom amenities.', 'Breakfast is served in the Chic & Basic’s modern snack bar, where you can also enjoy a cocktail. It is open 7 days a week from 08:00 until midnight.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Room Mate Pau! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Room Mate Pau is set 50 m from the emblematic Plaza Catalunya. It offers a stylish décor and a terrace and bright, contemporary rooms with free Wi-Fi.', 'Rooms at Room Mate Pau feature chic decor and air conditioning. All include a plasma TV with USB port for laptop connection, a mini-bar, safe and a modern private bathroom.', "A buffet breakfast is served daily, which you can enjoy at the property's shared terrace. Events can be catered for and various bars, restaurants and shops are within 2 minutes’ walk.", 'Other facilities include meeting and conference rooms.', 'Room Mate Pau is 2 minutes’ walk from Las Ramblas and Passeig de Gracia, with its exclusive shops and Gaudí monuments. Urquinaona Metro station is 150 m away, 2 stops from Barceloneta and its beach.', 'The hotel can help book tickets and activities and is 250 m from Catalunya Metro and FGC Train Station.']

hotel_description: ["You're eligible for a Genius discount at Catalonia Port! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.", 'Located in Barcelona’s Gothic Quarter, Hotel Catalonia Port has a modern gym and a sun terrace with a small seasonal outdoor pool. Each air-conditioned room has free WiFi, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels.', 'The hotel’s contemporary El Racó del Port restaurant opens from Monday to Saturday, serving seasonal Mediterranean cuisine. A varied buffet breakfast, available until 12:00 at the weekends, is offered in the dining room, and there is also a lobby bar.', 'The Catalonia Port Hotel offers stylish rooms with hardwood floors. They all include a safe, a mini-bar and a private bathroom.', 'Catalonia Port is just 250 m from the bottom of the famous Las Ramblas, and Port Vell Harbor is 400 m away. Drassanes Metro Station is a 5-minute walk away.']
